ch%20emerged%20as%20the%20top%20purchaser%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20-%20donated%20Rs%20509%20crore%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20ruling%20party%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam.%20The%20DMK%20received%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%20656.5%20crore%20under%20the%20now-scrapped%20electoral%20bonds%20system%2C%20which%20allowed%20anonymous%20and%20unlimited%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20data%20showed%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFuture%20Gaming%20purchased%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%201%2C368%20crore%2C%20of%20which%20nearly%2037%20per%20cent%20went%20to%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20or%20DMK.%20Megha%20Engineering%20(Rs%20105%20crore)%2C%20India%20Cements%20(Rs%2014%20crore)%20and%20Sun%20TV%20(Rs%2010%20crore)%20were%20other%20major%20donors%20of%20the%20DMK%20which%20was%20among%20the%20few%20political%20parties%20to%20disclose%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFresh%20Data%20On%20Electoral%20Bonds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20today%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpoll-panel-releases-fresh-data-on-funding-to-politiacal-parties-through-electoral-bonds-5255720%5C%22%3Epublic%20fresh%20data%20on%20electoral%20bonds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20it%20had%20submitted%20in%20sealed%20covers%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20was%20later%20asked%20to%20put%20it%20in%20public%20domain.%20These%20details%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20from%20the%20period%20before%20April%2012%2C%202019.%20Electoral%20bond%20details%20after%20this%20date%20were%20made%20public%20by%20the%20poll%20panel%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%20had%20filed%20data%20on%20Electoral%20Bonds%20in%20sealed%20cover%20as%20directed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20interim%20order%20dated%20April%2012%2C%202019%2C%20the%20poll%20panel%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20data%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20was%20the%20biggest%20overall%20recipient%20(Rs%206%2C986.5%20crore)%20of%20the%20bonds%20since%20they%20were%20introduced%20in%202018.%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20was%20the%20second%20biggest%20recipient%20(Rs%201%2C397%20crore)%20followed%20by%20Congress%20(Rs%201%2C334%20crore)%2C%20BRS%20(Rs%201%2C322%20crore)%20and%20Odisha's%20ruling%20party%20BJD%20at%20Rs%20944.5.%20The%20DMK%20was%20the%20sixth%20biggest%20recipient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Santiago%20Martin%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESantiago%20Martin's%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20purchased%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%201%2C368%20crore%20between%202019%20and%202024%20-%2040%25%20more%20than%20the%20next-highest%20donor%2C%20according%20to%20data%20uploaded%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20on%20its%20website%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Martin%20built%20a%20lottery-to-real%20estate%20empire%20up%20from%20selling%20lottery%20tickets%20as%20a%20teenager.%20He%20worked%20as%20a%20teenage%20labourer%20in%20Myanmar%20to%20support%20his%20family%20and%20returned%20to%20India%20in%20the%20late%201980s%20and%20began%20his%20business%20career%20in%20Coimbatore%2C%20according%20to%20his%20nonprofit%20Martin%20Charitable%20Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20two-digit%20lottery%20gained%20popularity%20in%20the%20region%20and%20Mr%20Martin%20expanded%20to%20other%20states%20and%20eventually%20to%20neighbouring%20Bhutan%20and%20Nepal%2C%20where%20he%20had%20a%20monopoly%20on%20distributing%20the%20tickets%2C%20according%20to%20his%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20investigative%20agencies%20have%20searched%20his%20business%20premises%20and%20seized%20properties%20in%20connection%20with%20cases%20against%20him.%20His%20appeals%20against%20property%20seizures%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20were%20dismissed%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Martin%20has%20denied%20wrongdoing.%20His%20conglomerate%2C%20Martin%20Group%2C%20said%20in%20October%20the%20group%20and%20its%20firms%20obey%20the%20law%20and%20that%20Mr%20Martin%20was%20India's%20highest%20taxpayer%20in%20the%20financial%20year%20to%20March%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Case%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20scrapped%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20in%20a%20landmark%20verdict%20last%20month%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%20and%20ordered%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%2C%20the%20authorised%20financial%20institution%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20to%20submit%20the%20details%20of%20the%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20was%20first%20asked%20to%20submit%20the%20data%20by%20March%206%20but%20it%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20an%20extension%20till%20June%2030.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20junked%20the%20petition%20and%20ordered%20it%20to%20disclose%20the%20details%20by%20the%20close%20of%20business%20hours%20on%20March%2012.%20It%20also%20asked%20the%20poll%20body%20to%20publish%20the%20information%20on%20its%20website%20on%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710698580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fbpac2j6_santiago-martin-_625x300_15_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbiggest-electoral-bonds-purchaser-is-top-donor-for-this-party-5256751%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Lottery%20king'%20Santiago%20Martin's%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20-%20which%20emerged%20as%20the%20top%20purchaser%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20-%20donated%20Rs%20509%20crore%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20ruling%20party%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbiggest-electoral-bonds-purchaser-is-top-donor-for-this-party-5256751%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amp