was%20no%20order%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomebody%20came%20to%20our%20office%20on%2003-04-2019%20at%20Patna%20and%20handed%20over%20a%20sealed%20envelope%20and%20when%20it%20was%20opened%20we%20found%20a%20bunch%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20containing%2010%20bonds%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccordingly%2C%20as%20per%20gazette%20notification%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20we%20opened%20an%20account%20in%20SBI%20Main%20Branch%2C%20Patna%2C%20and%20deposited%20it%2C%20which%20was%20credited%20to%20our%20party%20account%20on%2010-04-2019.%20In%20this%20view%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20provide%20any%20more%20details%20about%20the%20donors%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20JD(U)%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20submission%2C%20the%20party%20listed%20Shri%20Cement%20and%20Bharti%20Airtel%20as%20its%20other%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20its%20filing%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20disclosed%20total%20donations%20worth%20Rs%2010.84%20crore%2C%20of%20which%2C%20it%20said%2C%2010%20bonds%2C%20totalling%20Rs%2010%20crore%2C%20was%20received%20%26quot%3Bby%20post%20(no%20name)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20remainder%20amount%2C%20the%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20party%20listed%20S%20K%20traders%2C%20San%20Beverages%2C%20A%20K%20Traders%2C%20K%20S%20Traders%2C%20B%20G%20Traders%20and%20AS%20Traders%20as%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710698520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F8cjmr8l8_rupee-generic-reuters_625x300_01_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgot-rs-10-crore-poll-bonds-anonymously-encashed-it-nitish-kumars-party-to-poll-body-5257657%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Nitish%20