0general%20secretary%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%20on%20Sunday%20said%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bexperiment%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20will%20be%20determined%20later%20how%20beneficial%20and%20effective%20it%20has%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Pratinidhi%20Sabha%20(ABPS)%20on%20Sunday%20re-elected%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%20for%20the%20post%20of%20'Sarkaryavah'%20(general%20secretary)%20for%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20on%20Thursday%20released%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20data%2C%20with%20a%20number%20of%20billionaire%20tycoons%20and%20lesser-known%20entities%20being%20among%20the%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20steel%20tycoon%20Lakshmi%20Mittal%20to%20billionaire%20Sunil%20Bharti%20Mittal's%20Airtel%2C%20Anil%20Agarwal's%20Vedanta%2C%20ITC%2C%20Mahindra%20and%20Mahindra%2C%20and%20lesser-known%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20were%20among%20the%20prominent%20buyers%20of%20the%20now-scrapped%20electoral%20bonds%20for%20making%20political%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20concerns%20being%20raised%20on%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20issue%20and%20claims%20that%20they%20were%20purchased%20to%20get%20favours%2C%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%20said%20the%20Sangh%20has%20not%20yet%20discussed%20about%20it%20as%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bexperiment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20done%20with%20checks%20and%20balances%20and%20it%20is%20not%20that%20electoral%20bonds%20have%20suddenly%20been%20introduced%20today%2C%20it%20(such%20scheme)%20was%20brought%20earlier%20also.%20Whenever%20a%20change%20is%20introduced%2C%20questions%20are%20raised.%20Questions%20were%20also%20raised%20when%20the%20EVMs%20(electronic%20voting%20machines)%20were%20introduced%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20natural%20that%20questions%20will%20be%20raised%20by%20people%20when%20new%20things%20come%20up.%20But%20time%20will%20tell%20how%20beneficial%20and%20effective%20the%20new%20system%20is.%20Hence%2C%20the%20Sangh%20thinks%20it%20should%20be%20left%20for%20experiment%2C%26quot%3B%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%2010-year%20rule%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20he%20said%20the%20RSS%20welcomes%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20resolution%20demanding%20its%20enactment%20was%20passed%20several%20years%20ago%20in%20the%20outfit's%20'Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Pratinidhi%20Sabha'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20implemented%20in%20(BJP-ruled)%20Uttarakhand.%20We%20would%20like%20it%20to%20be%20implemented%20across%20the%20country.%20But%20there%20are%20certain%20details%20like%20succession%2C%20adoption%2C%20marriage%20and%20other%20issues%20that%20need%20to%20be%20discussed%20and%20then%20they%20can%20move%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20have%20seen%20the%20progress%20the%20country%20has%20made%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20and%20even%20renowned%20international%20experts%20and%20political%20thinkers%20have%20reiterated%20that%20the%20current%20century%20is%20India's%20century%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20good%20must%20be%20happening%20for%20them%20to%20say%20this.%20Anyway%2C%20people%20will%20give%20their%20verdict%20on%20June%204%20(Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20vote%20counting%20day)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20query%20on%20whether%20the%20cut%20off%20date%20in%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20must%20be%20extended%20from%20the%20current%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20the%20RSS%20leader%20said%20it%20can%20be%20done%20by%20the%20authorities%20if%20the%20need%20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20disputes%20pertaining%20to%20the%20places%20of%20worship%20at%20Mathura%20and%20Kashi%2C%20he%20said%20Hindu%20saints%20and%20the%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%20have%20raised%20the%20issue%20and%20have%20also%20said%20the%20type%20of%20agitation%20depends%20on%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20done%20for%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20should%20not%20be%20done%20for%20everything.%20It%20is%20not%20necessary.%20The%20matter%20is%20in%20court.%20If%20it%20is%20resolved%20by%20the%20court%20then%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20agitation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindu%20society%20will%20do%20whatever%20has%20to%20be%20done%20regarding%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20religious-social%20leadership%2C%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%2C%20who%20was%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20query%20on%20the%20RSS'%20definition%20of%20%26quot%3Bminority%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20the%20concept%20is%20there%20in%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20need%20to%20(have)%20rethink%20over%20it.%20Because%2C%20this%20country%20belongs%20to%20all%20and%20the%20method%20or%20idea%20of%20calling%20(communities)%20minority%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20decades.%20Those%20who%20are%20Hindu%20in%20the%20traditional%20sense%2C%20those%20who%20are%20considered%20as%20Hindus%20as%20per%20the%20Hindu%20Code%20Bill%2C%20are%20organized%20by%20the%20Sangh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20are%20considered%20minorities%20in%20India%2C%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20RSS%20has%20always%20opposed%20the%20politics%20of%20minoritism.%20The%20country%20is%20one%20and%20this%20is%20how%20it%20should%20continue%20is%20what%20the%20Sangh%20always%20says.%26quot%3B%20The%20annual%20three-day%20'Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Pratinidhi%20Sabha'%20of%20the%20RSS%20began%20at%20the%20'Smriti%20Bhavan'%20complex%20in%20Reshimbagh%20area%20of%20Maharashtra's%20Nagpur%20city%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20is%20taking%20place%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20the%20headquarters%20o