2%3A1710694506000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F136EA%2Fproduction%2F_132949597_67bf4fcbe1e53f9bb3da5f3ddb11e8edfd8492540_286_5500_30941000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68591539%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BBC%20speaks%20to%20Haitians%20who%20braved%20a%20treacherous%20journey%20out%20of%20Port-au-Prince%20as%20hunger%20worsens.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68591539%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68591539.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68591539.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Big%20Opposition%20Rally%20In%20Mumbai%2C%20A%20Mention%20Of%20Putin%20To%20Slam%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20ended%20his%2063-day-long%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20also%20met%20in%20the%20city%20today%2C%20where%20they%20stressed%20on%20the%20need%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20Mahagathbandhan%26quot%3B.%20The%20yatra%20had%20started%20from%20violence-hit%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20fighting%20against%20a%20person%20or%20a%20party.%20There%20is%20a%20word%20'Shakti'%20in%20Hinduism.%20We%20are%20fighting%20against%20that%20Shakti%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%20for%20its%20alleged%20use%20of%20central%20agencies%20and%20EVMs%20(electronic%20voting%20machines)%20against%20the%20opposition%2C%20he%20said%20the%20ruling%20party%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20win%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20without%20%26quot%3BEVMs%2C%20ED%20(Enforcement%20Directorate)%20and%20CBI%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20at%20Mumbai's%20Shivaji%20Park%20helmed%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20saw%20several%20Opposition%20leaders%20in%20attendance%2C%20including%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20and%20Mehbooba%20Mufti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElection%20dates%20have%20been%20announced...%20We%20have%20all%20come%20to%20Mumbai%20today.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20sent%20an%20invitation%2C%26quot%3B%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20rally%20at%20Shivaji%20Park%20is%20being%20billed%20as%20the%20biggest-ever%20show%20of%20strength%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20entire%20Gandhi%20family%2C%20to%20launch%20the%20bloc's%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20president%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20citing%20presidential%20elections%20in%20Russia%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPutin%20is%20contesting%20an%20election%20in%20Russia%20but%20no%20one%20is%20in%20front%20of%20him.%20They%20(the%20BJP)%20want%20to%20create%20a%20similar%20situation%20here%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20was%20the%20final%20day%20of%20the%20Russian%20presidential%20election%20that%20is%20guaranteed%20to%20cement%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20gathering%2C%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20speaks%20of%20winning%20more%20than%20400%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20order%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution...%20People%20in%20the%20BJP%20are%20afraid%20of%20Gandhi%20in%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20taken%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Congress%20while%20campaigning%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20PM%20Modi%2C%20alluding%20to%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20said%20the%20Congress's%20agenda%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Buse%20and%20throw%26quot%3B%20its%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20NDA%20(National%20Democratic%20Alliance)%2C%20we%20take%20everyone%20along%2C%20but%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20the%20Congress%20party's%20only%20agenda%20is%20to%20use%20and%20throw%20allies.%20Today%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20to%20make%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20out%20of%20compulsion%2C%20but%20their%20thinking%20is%20that%20only%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20his%20turn%20came%20to%20speak%20at%20Shivaji%20Parj%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janaya%20Dal's%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20fight%20is%20not%20against%20PM%20Modi%20or%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20personally%2C%20but%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Bideology%20of%20hate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%2C%20who%20now%20heads%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%2C%20said%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20gave%20the%20'Quit%20India'%20call%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20so%20INDIA%20bloc's%20leaders%20should%20do%20the%20same%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20oust%20the%20BJP%20from%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUddhav%20Thackeray%20launched%20a%20direct%20attack%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20unite%2C%20dictatorship%20ends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20begin%20on%20April%2019%20and%20end%20on%20June%201%3B%20counting%20is%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710694320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fptcjhppg_india-bloc-meeting_625x300_17_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-rahul-gandhis-big-opposition-unity-push-in-mumbai-weeks-before-elections-5257292%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20ended%20his%2063-day-long%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20also%20met%20in%20th