the%20next%20seven-ten%20years%20to%20grow%20businesses%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20projected%20capital%20expenditure%20or%20capex%20for%202024-25%20(April%202024%20to%20March%202025)%20fiscal%20is%2040%25%20higher%20than%20what%20the%20portfolio%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20incurred%20in%20FY24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20analysts%2C%20the%20portfolio%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20incurred%20a%20capex%20of%20around%20%2410%20billion%20in%20FY24%20that%20ends%20on%20March%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20these%20investments%20will%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20exponential%20profit%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20had%20previously%20guided%20a%20%24100%20billion%20capex%20over%20the%20next%207-10%20years.%20Most%20of%20this%20investment%20is%20going%20to%20go%20into%20group%20fast%20growing%20businesses%20-%20renewable%2C%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%2070%25%20of%20the%20planned%20capex%20will%20go%20into%20its%20green%20portfolio%20-%20primarily%20renewable%20power%2C%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20green%20evacuation.%20Of%20the%20remaining%2030%25%2C%20the%20majority%20will%20be%20spent%20towards%20airports%20and%20ports%20businesses%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20calendar%20year%202023%2C%20the%20portfolio%20delivered%20a%20%249.5%20billion%20Ebitda%20(up%2034.4%25%20year-on-year)%2C%20while%20its%20net%20debt%20has%20reduced%20by%204%25%20from%20March%202023%20to%20September%202023%20(balance%20sheet%20figures%20are%20only%20declared%20half%20yearly).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20December%20quarter%2C%20Adani's%20portfolio%20reported%20record%20Ebitda%20growth%20of%2063.6%25%2C%20taking%20its%2012-month%20Ebitda%20to%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%20%249.5%20billion%20(Rs%2078%2C823%20crore)%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncreasing%20cash%20flows%20from%20fast%20growing%20profits%20have%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20mega-scale%20investments%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20net%20debt%20to%20Ebitda%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September%20was%202.5x%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20decline%20by%20the%20end%20of%20FY24%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20media%20statement%20released%20in%20February%2C%20the%20group%20said%20increasing%20cash%20flows%20from%20strong%20growth%20and%20robust%20credit%20profile%20has%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20unrivalled%20'Green%20Investment'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20school%20drop-out%2C%20group%20chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%20started%20out%20as%20a%20commodities%20trader%20and%20rose%20to%20become%20Asia's%20richest%20person%20with%20an%20empire%20spanning%20across%20ports%2C%20power%20generation%2C%20airports%2C%20mining%2C%20renewables%2C%20gas%2C%20data%20centres%2C%20media%20and%20cement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Adani%20Group%20is%20the%20world's%20second%20largest%20solar%20power%20company%2C%20it%20is%20the%20largest%20airport%20operator%20with%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20passenger%20traffic%20and%2040%25%20of%20air%20cargo%2C%20the%20largest%20ports%20and%20logistics%20company%20with%2030%25%20of%20national%20market%20share%2C%20largest%20integrated%20energy%20player%2C%20and%20the%20country's%20second%20largest%20cement%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20largest%20infrastructure%20conglomerate%20with%20showcase%20projects%20like%20Navi%20Mumbai%20Airport%2C%20Ganga%20Expressway%2C%20world's%20largest%20renewable%20park%20at%20Khavda%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Mundra%20Port%20has%20committed%20a%20%24100%20billion%20investment%20over%20the%20next%207-10%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20investment%20will%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20transforming%20India's%20energy%20and%20transportation%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20with%20strong%20emphasis%20on%20green%20energy%20transition%2C%20it%20will%20be%20allocating%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20this%20%24100%20billion%20to%20its%20green%20businesses%20including%20renewable%20power%2C%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20and%20green%20evacuation%20transmission%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conglomerate%20is%20building%20the%20world's%20largest%20renewable%20park%20at%20Khavda%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20spanning%20over%20530%20square%20kilometers%20-%20an%20area%20five%20times%20the%20size%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20portion%20of%20total%20investments%20is%20earmarked%20for%20expansion%20and%20development%20of%20its%20fast-growing%20airports%20business%20and%20ports%20business%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20portfolio%20boasting%20eight%20airports%20including%20the%20upcoming%20Navi%20Mumbai%20airport%20and%2014%20domestic%20ports%2C%20Adani%20wants%20to%20further%20solidify%20its%20presence%20in%20these%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710690060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fukoaimu8_adani-reuters_625x300_10_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fadani-group-plans-to-invest-rs-1-2-lakh-crore-in-portfolio-companies-in-fy25-5257444%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adani%20group%20plans%20to%20invest%20more%20than%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20crore%20across%20its%20portfolio%20companies%20that%20range%20from%20ports%20to%20energy%2C%20airports%2C%20commodities%2C%20cement%20and%20media%20in%20fiscal%20year%20starting%20April%201%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fadani-group-plans-to-invest-rs-1-2-lakh-crore-in-portfolio-companies-in-fy25-5257444%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2