%20the%20fans.%20India%20marched%20to%20the%20final%20as%20the%20only%20unbeaten%20side%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20only%20to%20go%20down%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Australia%20in%20the%20final%20hurdle.%20The%20defeat%20extended%20India's%20ICC%20trophy%20drought%2C%20with%20their%20last%20success%20at%20world%20stage%20dating%20back%20to%202013%20when%20they%20won%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20under%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E's%20leadership.%20The%20year%202023%20saw%20India%20lose%20two%20ICC%20finals%2C%20both%20to%20Australia.%20Last%20year%20in%20June%2C%20India%20also%20lost%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20side%20in%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WTC%20final%20was%20played%20just%20days%20after%20the%20IPL%202023%20final.%20This%20year%20too%20the%20cash-rich%20league%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20West%20Indies%20and%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20off-spinner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20admitted%20that%20the%20team%20is%20indeed%20witnessing%20an%20ICC%20trophy%20drought.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20on%20a%20drought%20to%20win%20ICC%20trophies%20for%20years%20now%20and%20have%20consistently%20been%20knocked%20out%20in%20the%20semis%20or%20finals.%20And%20this%20is%20yet%20another%20year%20where%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20follows%20the%20IPL%20final%20by%20just%20five%20days%2C%20like%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSV2Tfqh1sjs%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20season%20of%20IPL%20kicks%20off%20on%20Friday%2C%20March%2022%20with%20defending%20champions%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20taking%20on%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%20in%20the%20tournament%20opener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BCCI%20has%20only%20announced%20the%20schedule%20for%20the%20first%2021%20matches%2C%20owing%20to%20General%20Elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20General%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20in%20India%20from%2019%20April%202024%20to%201%20June%202024%2C%20as%20announced%20by%20the%20Elections%20Commission%20on%20Saturday.%20it%20will%20be%20held%20in%20seven%20different%20phases%20and%20the%20results%20will%20be%20announced%20on%204%20June%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20BCCI%20is%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20of%20organising%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20in%20the%20UAE.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20elections%20dates%20have%20now%20been%20announced%2C%20the%20BCCI%20could%20soon%20announce%20the%20dates%20of%20the%20remaining%20fixtures%2C%20and%20also%20take%20on%20call%20on%20the%20possible%20venue%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710688560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fg43i61bo_ravichandran-ashwin-bcci_625x300_13_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Ft20-world-cup-just-5-days-after-ipl-final-r-ashwin-sums-up-indias-cricket-schedule-chaos-5256165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20T20%20World%20Cup%20begins%20on%20June%201%2C%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20rumoured%20date%20of%20the%20IPL%202024%20final.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Noon%20against%20Putin%E2%80%99%3A%20Thousands%20of%20Russians%20prot