18%2C%202019%20to%20July%2026%2C%202023.%20Among%20political%20parties%2C%20AAP%20is%20the%2011th%20highest%20recipient%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20data%20made%20available%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Bajaj%20Group%20has%20donated%20Rs%203%20crores%20to%20AAP%20in%20three%20instalments%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20each%20%E2%80%93%20all%20on%20April%2010%2C%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bajaj%20group%20has%20donated%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%2048%20crores%20as%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20all%20political%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAAP%20is%20among%20the%20ten%20political%20parties%20that%20have%20disclosed%20their%20donors%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20top%20three%20recipients%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20and%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20have%20not%20yet%20disclosed%20the%20names%20of%20their%20donors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETorrent%20Pharmaceuticals%20Limited%20is%20the%20second%20highest%20donor%20to%20AAP%20having%20donated%20Rs%201%20crore%20on%20May%2015%2C%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Torrent%20group%20is%20the%2010th%20highest%20donor%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20all%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20has%20donated%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20184%20crores%2C%20according%20to%20data%20made%20available%20by%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fnews%2Fclose-to-modi-exempt-from-taxes-torrent-group-bought-electoral-bonds-worth-rs-185-cr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Torrent%20group%E2%80%99s%20chairman%20emeritus%20Sudhir%20Mehta%20is%20considered%20close%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202014%2C%20after%20Modi%20became%20prime%20minister%2C%20Torrent%20Pharmaceuticals%20was%20the%20first%20company%20to%20secure%20an%20exemption%20from%20price%20control%20for%20its%20newly%20developed%20drug%20under%20a%20new%20drug%20pricing%20policy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20that%20Mehta%20and%20Gautam%20Adani%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%2017-member%20delegation%20at%20the%20Indo-US%20CEO%20Forum%20between%20Barack%20Obama%20and%20Modi%20in%20Delhi%20in%20January%202015%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20delegation%20to%20Australia%20in%20November%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBG%20Shirke%20Construction%20Technology%20has%20also%20donated%20Rs%201%20crore%20to%20the%20AAP%20on%20May%2021%2C%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20based%20construction%20company%20has%20donated%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20117%20crores%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20is%20the%2013th%20highest%20donor%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20data%20has%20revealed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBG%20Shirke%20Construction%20Technology%20describes%20itself%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20constructor%20of%20housing%20in%20India%20on%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshirkegroup.com%2Fdivisions%2Fcivil-division-2%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20website%20also%20lists%20the%20Mumbai%20Housing%20Area%20and%20Development%20Board%20(MHADA)%2C%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20(DDA)%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Housing%20Board%2C%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%2C%20Bangalore%20Development%20Authority%20(BDA)%2C%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20(DDA)%2C%20Karnataka%20Housing%20Board%2C%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%20(AAI)%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Rajiv%20Swagruha%20Corporation%20Limited%2C%20among%20others%2C%20as%20its%20clients.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20third%20highest%20donor%20to%20AAP%20is%20KMZ%20Investment%20that%20donated%20Rs%2050%20lakh%2C%C2%A0%20in%20five%20separate%20donations%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20each%2C%20on%20April%2012%2C%202019.%20According%20to%20zaubacorp.com%2C%20the%20company%20is%20involved%20in%20human%20health%20activities%20and%20is%20registered%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAAP%E2%80%99s%20fourth%20highest%20donor%20is%20NJK%20Enterprises%2C%20a%20Bengaluru%20based%20company%20that%20has%20donated%20Rs%2020%20lakhs%20on%20April%2018%2C%202019%20in%20two%20donations%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20each.%20According%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisilratings.com%2Fmnt%2Fwinshare%2FRatings%2FRatingList%2FRatingDocs%2FNJKEnterprises_February%252024%2C%25202023_RR_312692.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20CRISI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3EL%2C%20it%20is%20primarily%20involved%20in%20manufacture%20and%20export%20of%20ready%20made%20garments.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brickworkratings.com%2FAdmin%2FPressRelease%2FNJK-Enterprises_33.20Cr_Rationale_2-April-2018(1).pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egroup%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%C2%A0%20India%20Design%20Exports%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20remainder%20of%20its%20listed%20donations%20have%20come%20from%20individuals%20according%20to%20the%20donor%20names%20made%20available%20by%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710683377000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F18161034%2FScreen-Shot-2020-02-18-at-4.08.52-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbajaj-group-emerges-as-top-donor-to-aap-as-party-discloses-electoral-bond-donors-for-2018-2019%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20AAP%20has%20received%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%2065.45%20crores%20between%20April%2018%2C%202019%20and%20July%2026%2C%202023%2C%20it%20has%20only%