in%20Greece%E2%80%99s%20second%20city.%20Using%20both%20the%20director%E2%80%99s%20personal%20archives%20and%208mm%20recordings%20of%20strangers%E2%80%99%20lives%2C%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Postcardjunky%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fmy-stolen-planet-thessaloniki-documentary-festival-1235944087%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fmy-stolen-planet-thessaloniki-documentary-festival-1235944087%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fmy-stolen-planet-thessaloniki-documentary-festival-1235944087%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Quest%20for%20Identity%3A%20The%20Story%20of%20Indian%20Indentured%20Labourers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F29103240%2FGirmitiyas-in-Trinidad-public-domain.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20tribute%20to%20this%20extraordinary%20work%2C%20the%20author%2C%20Ambassador%20Bhaswati%20Mukherjee%20could%20deservedly%20add%20%E2%80%98Dr.%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Prof.%E2%80%99%20to%20her%20diplomatic%20designation.%20Her%20labour%20of%20love%20would%20easily%20pass%20muster%20as%20a%20doctoral%20thesis%20at%20the%20best%20universities.%20Evidence%20of%20her%20scholarship%20is%20to%20be%20found%20in%20the%20370%20footnotes%20that%20adorn%20the%20198%20pages%20of%20her%20thesis.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20range%20from%20English%20to%20French%20sources%2C%20a%20language%20in%20which%20she%20is%20effortlessly%20fluent%2C%20and%20even%20Dutch%20(she%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20Ambassador%20to%20The%20Hague)%20besides%20Hindi%20and%20Bhojpuri.%20They%20cover%20a%20wide%20swathe%20of%20research%20that%20reveal%20both%20her%20dedication%20to%20her%20subject%20as%20well%20as%20her%20diligence%20in%20winkling%20out%20facts%20and%20opinions%20from%20virtually%20all%20available%20sources.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20earliest%20of%20these%20sources%20date%20back%20to%20the%201812%20report%20of%20a%20select%20committee%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20and%20a%20selection%20of%20papers%20from%20the%20records%20of%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20published%20by%20J.E.Cox%20in%201820%2C%20leading%20up%20to%20the%201871%20Report%20of%20the%20Commissioners%20looking%20into%20the%20treatment%20of%20immigrants%20into%20British%20Guyana%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20John%20Fiske%E2%80%99s%20publication%20of%20his%20influential%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Unseen%20World%20and%20other%20Essays%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%201876.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20334px)%2085vw%2C%20334px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17184045%2F81QE6DcKy2L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22334%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17184045%2F81QE6DcKy2L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20645w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17184045%2F81QE6DcKy2L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-194x300.jpg%20194w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702101%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22518%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBhaswati%20Mukherjee%2C%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indentured%20and%20Their%20Route%3A%20A%20Relentless%20Quest%20for%20Identity%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ERupa%2C%20New%20Delhi%20(2023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20then%20on%2C%20books%20and%20reports%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20indentured%20labour%20become%20prolific%2C%20notably%20Dadabhai%20Naoroji%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPoverty%20and%20Un-British%20Rule%20in%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0(1860s)%3B%20Major%20D.G.%20Pilcher%E2%80%99s%201883%20report%20on%20the%20system%20of%20recruiting%20labour%20for%20emigration%3B%20the%201894%20report%20of%20the%20Protector%20of%20Emigrants%20on%20the%20excessively%20high%20death%20rates%20at%20the%20Calcutta%20depot%3B%20and%20the%201897%20proceedings%20of%20a%20conference%20on%20indentured%20labour%20convened%20in%20London%20by%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20the%20colonies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20turn%20of%20the%2019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%2C%20the%20question%20of%20indentured%20labour%20had%20become%20an%20acute%20source%20of%20concern%2C%20dissatisfaction%20and%20dissent%20for%20not%20only%20Indian%20nationalists%20of%20the%20standing%20of%20Gopalkrishna%20Gokhale%20and%20Lokmanya%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak%20but%20also%20the%20rising%20stars%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%20from%20Gandhi%20to%20Jinnah.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20lead%20to%20one%20of%20the%20more%20humane%20and%20sensitive%20of%20British%20viceroys%2C%20Lord%20Hardinge%2C%20to%20recommend%2C%20in%20virtually%20his%20last%20report%20home%20from%20India%20in%201917%2C%20that%20the%20whole%20question%20of%20indentured%20labour%20be%20reviewed%20by%20the%20Imperial%20government.%20Although%20this%20was%20not%20followed%20up%20by%20his%20successor%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%E2%80%98cold%E2%80%99%20Lord%20Chelmsford%2C%20as%20the%20author%20describes%20him%20%E2%80%93%20by%201924%2C%20the%20liberal%20opinion%20in%20the%20British%20parliament%20was%20sufficiently%20outraged%20to%20outlaw%20indenture%20even%20as%20they%20had%20outlawed%20slavery%20a%20century%20earlier%20%E2%80%93%20only%20to%20replace%20slavery%20by%20indenture!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20that%20indenture%20stands%20abolished%20since%20exactly%20a%20century%2C%20academic%20work%20of%20a%20high%20order%20has%20studied%20its%20origins%20and%20its%20similarity%20to%20slavery%20despite%20a%20contract%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egirmit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20between%20the%20employer%20and%20the%20labour.%20However%2C%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20the%20indentured%20could%20neither%20read%2C%20understand%20or%20even%20sign%20the%20document%20%E2%80%93%20they%20only%20affixed%20their%20thumb%20print%20on%20it%20%E2%80%93%20resulting%20in%20gross%20violation%2C%20by%20the%20white%20employers%2C%20of%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20contract%20as%20well%20as%20ignoring%20its%20provisions%20for%20the%20welfare%20and%20repatriation%20of%20these%20allegedly%20%E2%80%98voluntary%E2%80%99%20emigres%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egirmitiya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20they%20termed%20themselves.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPut%20to%20backbreaking%20labour%20for%20up%20to%2020%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20supervised%20by%20brutal%2C%20whip-cracking%20overseers%2C%20the%20indentured%20were%20effectively%20deprived%20of%20all%20rights%20and%2C%20like%20the%20slaves%20earlier%2C%20tied%20forever%20to%20their%20masters.%20Women%20were%20hugely%20discriminated%20against%2C%20their%20honour%20repeatedly%20violated%2C%20their%20marital%20status%20left%20indeterminate%2C%20their%20wages%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20the%20menfolk%20were%20paid.%20Living%20and%20sanitary%20conditions%20were%20terrible%20resulting%20in%20massive%20loss%20of%20life%20at%20a%20young%20age%20and%20among%20infants%2C%20as%20well%20as%20high%20maternal%20mortality.%20Ambassador%20Mukherjee%20describes%20all%20this%20pain%20and%20suffering%20with%20both%20passion%20and%20compassion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20lends%20dignity%20to%20this%20otherwise%20sordid%20tale%20is%20that%20notwithstanding%20their%20having%20left%20their%20homeland%20thousands%20of%20miles%20across%20the%20distant%20oceans%2C%20never%20to%20return%2C%20this%20reluctant%20diaspora%2C%20forced%20by%20poverty%20and%20despair%20out%20of%20their%20native%20milieu%2C%20struggled%20to%20preserve%20the%20collective%20community%20memory%20of%20their%20religious%20and%20cultural%20practices.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20author%20illustrates%20this%20with%20excellent%20translations%20from%20the%20original%20Bhojpuri%20of%20their%20songs%20and%20stories.%20Despite%20the%20odds%2C%20they%20held%20on%20to%20their%20identity.%20Of%20course%2C%20back%20home%2C%20several%20of%20these%20traditional%20rites%20and%20rituals%2C%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20religious%20beliefs%20were%20changing%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20perhaps%20why%20diaspora%20writers%20of%20high%20distinction%2C%20of%20whom%20V.S.%20Naipaul%20is%20the%20most%20famous%2C%20critique%20a%20distant%20memory%20of%20their%20home%20country%20without%20absorbing%20the%20profound%20transformations%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20since%20their%20ancestors%20of%20nearly%20200%20years%20ago%20exchanged%20poverty%20for%20degradation%20in%20the%20false%20expectation%20that%20they%20would%20be%20making%20a%20better%20life%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20children.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20this%20unending%20%E2%80%9Cquest%20for%20identity%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20made%20of%20the%20descendants%20of%20indentured%20labour%2C%20a%20diaspora%20spreading%20from%20the%20South%20Pacific%20right%20around%20the%20world%20through%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20to%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20the%20most%20distinctive%20diaspora%20the%20world%20has%20ever%20known%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CIndian%E2%80%9D%20despite%20being%20deprived%20of%20India%20for%20years%20and%20years%20and%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmbassador%20Mukherjee%20draws%20on%20the%20vast%20literature%20spawned%20in%20recent%20times%20to%20study%20the%20trials%20and%20tribulations%20of%20the%20indentured%20until%20liberation%20came.%20Her%20two%20most%20quoted%20scholars%20are%20Hugh%20Tinker%2C%20who%20wrote%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3EA%20New%20System%20of%20Slavery%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Export%20of%20Indian%20Labour%20Overseas%20(1993)%2C%20and%20Brij%20V.%20Lal%2C%20from%20his%20full%20range%20of%20writings%20in%20books%20and%20leaned%20journals.%20But%20her%20research%20is%20far%20from%20limited%20to%20these%20principal%20sources.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20can%20be%20seen%20from%20her%20meticulous%20footnotes%20and%20her%20impressive%20(but%20disappointingly%20incomplete)%20Bibliography%2C%20she%20delves%20deep%20and%20wide%20into%20available%20records%20and%20garnishes%20her%20tales%20with%20cameo%20portraits%20of%20those%20who%20went%20over%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekalapani%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20work%20the%20sugar%20plantations%20%E2%80%93%20not%20%E2%80%9Cvoluntarily%E2%80%9D%20but%20driven%20by%20desperation%2C%20bewildered%20and%20mercilessly%20exploited.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHappily%2C%20their%20struggle%20for%20liberation%20in%20concert%20with%20their%20sympathisers%20in%20India%20and%20Great%20Britain%20came%20to%20final%20success%20in%201924%20with%20the%20abolition%20of%20indentured%20labour%20by%20the%20British%20Parliament.%20It%20is%20a%20heroic%20and%20inspiring%20tale%20told%20with%20verve%20and%20profound%20empathy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReassuringly%2C%20in%20many%20of%20the%20host%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20notably%20Mauritius%2C%20Trinidad%2C%20Guyana%20and%20Suriname%20%E2%80%93%20the%20descendants%20of%20the%20indentured%20rose%20to%20high%20political%20positions.%20The%20names%20of%20Sir%20Seewosaugur%20Ramgoolam%20of%20Mauritius%20and%20his%20family%3B%20of%20Bishnu%20Pandey%20and%20Ranjit%20Kumar%20of%20Trinidad%3B%20of%20Sridath%20Ramphal%20of%20Guyana%3B%20of%20Shankar%20and%20Rabin%20S.%20Baldewsingh%20of%20Suriname%3B%20and%20Reddy%20of%20Fiji%20readily%20come%20to%20mind.%20Perhaps%20it%20was%20in%20Reunion%20and%20other%20French%20colonies%20that%20the%20nexus%20between%20the%20immigrant%20and%20the%20home%20country%20was%20most%20effectively%20snapped.%20Elsewhere%2C%20it%20was%2C%20as%20the%20author%20says%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Crelentless%20quest%20for%20identity%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20main%20cautionary%20tale%20for%20contemporary%20India%20that%20comes%20through%20is%20that%20where%20our%20diaspora%20integrated%20with%20local%20communities%20and%20culture%20without%20abandoning%2C%20indeed%20enhancing%20our%20grand%20civilisational%20tradition%20of%20%E2%80%9Cabsorption%2C%20assimilation%20and%20synthesis%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20in%20Mauritius%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20thrived%2C%20but%20where%20it%20consciously%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20locals%2C%20as%20in%20Fiji%2C%20inter-community%20tensions%20persist.%20Apartheid%2C%20that%20is%2C%20%E2%80%9Cliving%20apart%E2%80%9D%2C%20does%20not%20work.%20So%20also%2C%20within%20our%20nation%2C%20it%20is%20not%20through%20uniformity%20that%20we%20will%20best%20achieve%20unity.%20It%20is%20only%20%E2%80%98unity%20in%20diversity%E2%80%99%20that%20will%20ensure%20our%20emotional%20integration%20as%20a%20free%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710681162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F29103240%2FGirmitiyas-in-Trinidad-public-domain.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-quest-for-identity-the-story-of-indian-indentured-labourers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Put%20to%20backbreaking%20labour%20for%20up%20to%2020%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20supervised%20by%20brutal%2C%20whip-cracking%20overseers%2C%20the%20indentured%20were%20effectively%20deprived%20of%20all%20rights%20and%2C%20like%20the%20slaves%20earlier%2C%20tied%20forever%20to%20their%20masters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-quest-for-identity-the-story-of-indian-indentured-labourers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20an%20Irish%20American%20who%20visited%20the%20oldest%20Irish%20tavern%20in%20New%20York%20City%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Here%20are%209%20things%20that%20surprised%20me.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22892%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcsorleys%20ale%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f4a54a3037f8e81750f575%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20surprised%20by%20my%20experience%20at%20McSorley's%20Old%20Ale%20House.%3Cp%3EJames%20Kirkikis%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAhead%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbest-irish-pub-in-every-state-yelp%5C%22%3ESt.%20Patrick's%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20visited%20McSorley's%20Old%20Ale%20House%2C%20which%20was%20established%20in%201854.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20inexpensive%20prices%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20food.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20was%20also%20surprised%20by%20how%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20pride%20as%20an%20Irish%20American.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lived%20in%20New%20York%20City%20for%20almost%20four%20years%2C%20but%20I%20have%20never%20been%20to%20McSorley's%2C%20the%20oldest%20Irish%20pub%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcsorleys-bar-history-beer-photos-2017-11%5C%22%3EMcSorley's%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20most%20historic%20Irish%20tavern%20in%20New%20York%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20often%20called%20the%20oldest%20Irish%20tavern%20in%20America%20that's%20still%20in%20operation.%20Established%20in%201854%2C%20McSorley's%20is%20celebrating%20its%20170th%20anniversary%20this%20year%2C%20and%20it%20is%20certainly%20the%20place%20to%20go%20around%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20famous%2C%20McSorley's%20hasn't%20always%20been%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20history.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1970%2F08%2F11%2Farchives%2Fmcsorleys-admits-women-under-a-new-city-law-mcsorleys-is-forced-to.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20women%20have%20only%20been%20allowed%20inside%20the%20bar%20since%201970%2C%20when%20two%20members%20of%20the%20National%20Organization%20for%20Women%20sued%20the%20bar%20for%20violating%20the%20equal-protection%20ordinance%20of%20the%2014th%20Amendment.%20There%20were%20also%20no%20female%20bartenders%20until%20the%20mid-'90s%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbedfordandbowery.com%2F2020%2F12%2Fmcsorleys-first-female-bartender-keeps-its-spirit-alive%2Famp%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBedford%20%2B%20Bowery%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%202023%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20visit%20the%20bar%20given%20its%20rich%20history%20and%20connection%20to%20my%20heritage.%20My%20grandparents%20were%20first-generation%20Irish%20immigrants%20who%20later%20moved%20to%20England.%20That%20fact%2C%20in%20combination%20with%20my%20very%20Irish%20name%2C%20makes%20me%20proud%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraditional-irish-breakfast-recipe-review-st-patricks-day-2022-3%5C%22%3Eclose%20connection%20to%20my%20heritage.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20I%20enjoyed%20my%20experience%20at%20McSorley's%20during%20my%20visit%20last%20year.%20Here%20are%20some%20things%20that%20might%20surprise%20you%20about%20the%20oldest%20Irish%20bar%20in%20the%20country%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20visit%20yourself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20surprised%20by%20McSorley's%20location%20in%20a%20very%20modern%20section%20of%20the%20East%20Village.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcsorleys%20old%20ale%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64145ae05f4f5400191a0c9e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20outside%20of%20McSorley's.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20expected%20to%20find%20McSorley's%20on%20a%20quaint%20cobblestone%20street%20given%20its%20history%2C%20it's%20located%20in%20a%20built-up%20section%20of%20the%20East%20Village%20on%20East%207th%20Street%2C%20by%20Astor%20Place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20actually%20lived%20around%20the%20corner%20for%20a%20semester%20in%20college%2C%20and%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20this%20part%20of%20the%20East%20Village%20has%20very%20little%20old-world%20charm%20thanks%20to%20its%20high-rise%20buildings%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20chain%20restaurants%2C%20despite%20being%20just%20a%20stone's%20throw%20away%20from%20one%20of%20the%20most%20historic%20establishments%20in%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20the%20ale%20house%20was%20founded%20by%20Irish%20immigrant%20John%20McSorley%20in%20the%201850s%2C%20this%20was%20a%20prime%20location%2C%20close%20to%20a%20transportation%20hub%20for%20horse%20carriages%20and%20a%20busy%20market%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcsorleys-bar-history-beer-photos-2017-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMcSorley's%20is%20cash-only%2C%20which%20I%20learned%20when%20I%20arrived.%20However%2C%20you'll%20find%20an%20ATM%20right%20out%20front.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcsorleys%20old%20ale%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64145b140308e00018553195%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20ATM%20outside%20McSorley's.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20pretty%20standard%20at%20any%20cash-only%20bar%20or%20restaurant%20in%20New%20York%20City%20to%20find%20an%20ATM%20either%20inside%20or%20just%20outside%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20pleased%20that%20they%20had%20an%20ATM%20available%20so%20close%20by%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20spy%20any%20signs%20inside%20that%20made%20it%20immediately%20apparent%20it%20was%20cash-only%20%E2%80%94%20I%20didn't%20suss%20it%20out%20until%20I%20saw%20everyone%20else%20paying%20in%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20expected%20to%20find%20a%20lot%20of%20Irish%20pub%20food%2C%20and%20I%20did%2C%20but%20McSorley's%20also%20had%20distinctly%20American%20foods%20like%20hot%20dogs%20and%20hamburgers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223379%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcsorleys%20old%20ale%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F641460175f4f5400191a0d56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222534%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20menu%20at%20McSorley's.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20menu%20at%20McSorley's%20is%20limited%2C%20but%20they%20had%20quite%20a%20few%20fan-favorite%20menu%20items%2C%20from%20burgers%20and%20a%20fried-chicken%20sandwich%20to%20more%20traditional%20items%20like%20corned-beef%20hash%20and%20chili.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20surprised%20by%20how%20low%20the%20prices%20were%20at%20McSorley's%20compared%20to%20what%20I%20usually%20pay%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20I%20ordered%20a%20hamburger%20and%20fries%20for%20%2410%2C%20and%20two%20beers%20for%20%248.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20overall%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20the%20burger%20at%20McSorley's%2C%20but%20I%20wish%20the%20cheese%20had%20been%20more%20melted.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcsorleys%20old%20ale%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64145b085f4f5400191a0cb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cheeseburger%20at%20McSorley's.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20visited%20McSorley's%2C%20the%20bar%20was%20teeming%20with%20people%20and%20there%20were%20very%20few%20places%20to%20sit.%20I'm%20always%20a%20little%20hesitant%20about%20ordering%20bar%20food%20%E2%80%93%20you%20just%20never%20know%20what%20you're%20going%20to%20get%2C%20especially%20from%20places%20popular%20with%20tourists%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20I%20liked%20the%20burger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beef%20patty%20was%20juicy%20and%20decently%20large%2C%20while%20the%20onions%20and%20tomatoes%20tasted%20very%20fresh.%20The%20fries%20were%20also%20piping%20hot%20when%20I%20received%20them%20and%20deliciously%20crispy.%20The%20only%20downside%20in%20my%20opinion%20was%20that%20the%20cheese%20on%20the%20cheeseburger%20wasn't%20melted%20on%20the%20patty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20%2410%2C%20I%20was%20pleased%20with%20my%20dinner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMcSorley's%20has%20only%20two%20options%20for%20alcoholic%20drinks%20%E2%80%94%20light%20or%20dark%20beer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20serve%20two%20at%20a%20time%20per%20person%2C%20which%20definitely%20surprised%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcsorleys%20old%20ale%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64145b1f5f4f5400191a0cc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20beer%20at%20McSorley's.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20paid%20%248%20for%20two%20beers%2C%20a%20light%20and%20a%20dark%20ale%2C%20which%20I%20was%20surprised%20by.%20I'm%20not%20a%20huge%20beer%20drinker%2C%20but%20even%20that%20seemed%20pretty%20inexpensive%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beer%20prices%20have%20crept%20up%20over%20the%20years%2C%20of%20course.%20When%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcsorleys-bar-history-beer-photos-2017-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Sarah%20Jacobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20visited%20in%202017%2C%20the%20beer%20cost%20%245.50.%20She%20noted%20that%20the%20beer%20cost%20only%20a%20dime%20per%20mug%20in%201940%2C%20and%20in%201966%2C%20two%20of%20the%20half-pints%20cost%2035%20cents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20guests%20also%20appeared%20to%20be%20surprised%20by%20their%20orders.%20When%20one%20guest%20ordered%20a%20light%20and%20a%20dark%20beer%20for%20himself%20and%20someone%20else%2C%20they%20seemed%20surprised%20when%20they%20were%20each%20handed%20two%20beers.%20The%20bartender%20then%20explained%20that%20they%20always%20give%20people%20two%20beers%20each.%20The%20beers%20are%20much%20smaller%20than%20your%20average%20pint.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fny.eater.com%2F2022%2F11%2F17%2F23462867%2Fmcsorleys-irish-saloon-cheap-beer-prices-nyc-restaurants%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEater%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20each%20mug%20holds%20roughly%206%20ounces%20per%20glass%20%E2%80%94%20a%20US%20pint%20holds%2016%20ounces%20%E2%80%94%20which%20makes%20each%20drink%20easier%20to%20finish%20and%20carry%20around%20the%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20enjoyed%20both%20the%20light%20and%20the%20dark%20ale%2C%20though%20I%20preferred%20the%20light%2C%20and%20thought%20they%20went%20down%20smoothly.%20I%20could%20see%20why%20someone%20would%20want%20two%20at%20a%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20charm%20of%20McSorley's%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20low%20prices%2C%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20choice.%20In%20a%20city%20like%20New%20York%2C%20I'm%20accustomed%20to%20lengthy%20drink%20menus%20with%20steep%20prices.%20I%20actually%20enjoyed%20the%20lack%20of%20choice%2C%20which%20made%20ordering%20fast%20and%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20also%20surprised%20by%20just%20how%20much%20history%20was%20crammed%20onto%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20walls.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcsorleys%20old%20ale%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64145b350308e0001855319c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPictures%20hanging%20on%20the%20walls%20inside%20McSorley's.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20inch%20of%20the%20walls%20was%20adorned%20with%20old%20photos%2C%20newspaper%20clippings%2C%20pictures%20of%20Irish%20American%20presidents%2C%20and%20festive%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20decorations.%20A%20large%20flag%20hung%20behind%20the%20bar%20with%20the%20number%20169%20on%20it%20%E2%80%94%20the%20number%20of%20years%20the%20bar%20has%20been%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bar%20is%20also%20home%20to%20a%20few%20other%20historical%20mementos%20like%20Houdini's%20handcuffs%20and%20World%20War%20I-era%20wishbones%20dangling%20from%20a%20gas%20lamp%20above%20the%20bar.%20US%20Presidents%20Abraham%20Lincoln%2C%20Ulysses%20S.%20Grant%2C%20and%20Theodore%20Roosevelt%20also%20reportedly%20stopped%20by%20McSorley's%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnewyork.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fthe-east-villages-historic-mcsorleys-old-ale-house%2F410266%2F%3Famp%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20NBC%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20joint's%20historic%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20have%20spent%20hours%20looking%20at%20every%20piece%20of%20art%20and%20history%2C%20and%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20pride%20in%20my%20Irish%20heritage.%20It%20felt%20as%20if%20I%20were%20in%20a%20living%20time%20capsule%2C%20surrounded%20by%20people%20who%20were%20there%20for%20a%20great%20time%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20historic%20spots%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20bartender%20who%20served%20me%20was%20Irish%2C%20making%20for%20an%20even%20more%20authentic%20experience.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcsorleys%20old%20ale%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414645e5f4f5400191a0dc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBehind%20the%20bar%20at%20McSorley's.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20how%20busy%20the%20bar%20was%2C%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20the%20friendly%20and%20fast%20service%20I%20received%20from%20the%20bar%20staff%20and%20bouncer.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20an%20immersive%20experience%2C%20you%20can't%20feel%20much%20closer%20to%20Ireland%20anywhere%20other%20than%20McSorley's.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20you're%20unable%20to%20grab%20a%20spot%20inside%2C%20the%20restaurant%20has%20plenty%20of%20outdoor%20seating.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcsorleys%20old%20ale%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64145b610308e000185531a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20outdoor%20seating%20at%20McSorley's.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20surprised%20that%20a%20few%20days%20before%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%2C%20finding%20a%20spot%20to%20sit%20inside%20the%20restaurant%20at%20prime%20time%20was%20a%20little%20difficult.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20find%20that%20as%20the%20night%20went%20on%20and%20it%20turned%208%20o'clock%2C%20tables%20started%20to%20open%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20large%20outdoor%20dining%20area%20set%20up%20on%20the%20street%20outside%2C%20so%20finding%20a%20place%20to%20sit%20on%20busy%20days%2