s%20website%20the%20submissions%20made%20by%20the%20political%20parties%20in%202023%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20that%20they%20had%20received%20through%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI).%20Those%20submissions%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20the%20top%20court%20by%20the%20commission%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthedailyguardian.com%2Fec-to-submit-electoral-bonds-details-to-sc-in-sealed-cover%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20sealed%20covers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20November%202023%20to%20maintain%20the%20confidentiality%20clause%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20brought%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20details%20furnished%20by%20the%20parties%20were%20from%20April%202019%20to%20November%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20DMK%20treasurer%20and%20party%20MP%20T.R.%20Baalu%E2%80%99s%20submission%20to%20the%20ECI%20on%20November%2011%2C%202023%2C%20the%20SBI%2C%20which%20had%20issued%20bonds%20to%20the%20buyers%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%9Crequire%20the%20details%20of%20the%20donor%20to%20be%20furnished%20to%20the%20donee%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20circumstances%2C%20the%20donors%20did%20not%20strictly%20adhere%20to%20the%20requirement%20of%20furnishing%20their%20details%20whenever%20they%20handed%20over%20the%20electoral%20bond%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Baluu%20had%20stated%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20adding%2C%20that%20the%20party%20was%2C%20however%2C%20able%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccollect%20the%20details%20from%20them%E2%80%9D%20on%20time%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20call.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20details%20in%20the%20submission%20showed%20that%20Santiago%20Martin%E2%80%99s%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20had%20donated%20Rs%2060%20crores%20to%20the%20DMK%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20between%20October%2023-29%2C%202020%20and%20a%20staggering%20Rs%20249%20crore%20between%20April%205%2C%202021%20and%20January%201%2C%202022.%20The%20DMK%20government%2C%20with%20M.K.%20Stalin%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20was%20formed%20after%20the%20April%202021%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202021-2022%20financial%20year%2C%20the%20Coimbatore-based%20company%20had%20picked%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20fund%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20for%20Rs%20309%20crores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20company%20pumped%20in%20more%20funds%20with%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%20185%20crores%20donated%20to%20the%20party%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20company%20once%20again%20donated%20Rs%2040%20crores%20to%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20submissions%2C%20between%202020%20and%202023%2C%20it%20donated%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20534%20crores%20to%20the%20DMK%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerusing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Felection-commission-uploads-electoral-bonds-data-on-website-as-per-supreme-courts-direction-252331%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20data%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20till%20January%202024%2C%20the%20Future%20Gaming%20group%2C%20having%20spent%20a%20cumulative%20sum%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fsantiago-martin-aka-lottery-king-the-business-tycoon-who-topped-the-list-of-electoral-bond-donors%2Farticle67953870.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERs%201%2C368%20crores%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20came%20across%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20donor%20to%20political%20parties%20through%20the%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20another%20company%2C%20Mega%20Infrastructure%20Developers%20Private%20Limited%2C%20registered%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Panchsheel%20Enclave%2C%20donated%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20105%20crores%20between%20April%202019%20and%202022%20to%20the%20DMK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20company%2C%20identified%20as%20only%20Triveni%2C%20had%20contributed%20to%20the%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20coffers%20Rs%208%20crores%20between%202019%20and%202022.%20A%20clasp%20of%20other%20companies%2C%20seemingly%20dealing%20with%20cement%20manufacturing%2C%20also%20donated%20a%20cumulative%20sum%20of%20Rs%2019%20crores%20to%20DMK%20through%20bonds.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Sun%20TV%20Network%20of%20Kalanidhi%20Maran%20also%20featured%20in%20the%20list%20of%20donors%2C%20having%20made%20a%20one-time%20payment%20of%20Rs%2010%20crores%20in%202021-22.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20total%20amount%20the%20party%20stated%20to%20have%20received%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20between%20April%202019%20and%20November%202023%20stood%20at%20Rs.%20706%20crores.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAIDMK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20freshly%20released%20data%2C%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20Cricket%20Limited%20donated%20Rs%205%20crores%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIDMK)%20party%20in%202019.%20The%20bonds%20purchased%20by%20India%20Cement%20Limited-owned%20CSK%20on%20April%203%2C%202019%20were%20encashed%20on%20the%2012th%20of%20the%20same%20month.%20Two%20bonds%20purchased%20were%20of%20denomination%20R.%201%20crore%20each%20and%20the%20rest%20were%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakhs%20each.%20The%20data%20also%20shows%20that%20India%20Cement%20donated%20as%20additional%20Rs%2010%20crores%20to%20the%20ruling%20MK%20Stalin-led%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarayanaswami%20Srinivasan%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20ICL%20has%20also%20been%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20and%20former%20President%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI).%20In%20September%20last%20year%2C%20Srinivasan%20and%20his%20family%20became%20the%20promoters%20of%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20Cricket%20Ltd.%20(CSK)%2C%20the%20designated%20owner%20of%20the%20Chennai%20team%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%20India%20Cements%E2%80%99%20annual%20report%20shows%20that%20Srinivasan%20and%20his%20family%20own%2028.14%25%20of%20CSK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20carried%20out%20raids%20at%20the%20office%20of%20India%20Cements%20Capital%20Limited%2C%20an%20associate%20company%20of%20ICL%2C%20for%20alleged%20violations%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%20(FEMA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20however%2C%20had%20termed%20the%20search%20as%20%E2%80%9Cnormal%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Findia-cements-says-ed-searches-related-to-normal-course-transactions%2Farticle67804436.ece%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20soon%20after%20the%20raid%2C%20ICL%20claimed%3A%20%E2%80%9CICCL%20is%20an%20authorised%20dealer%20in%20providing%20forex%20services%20and%20has%20been%20providing%20these%20services%20to%20its%20clients%20complying%20with%20rules%20framed%20by%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India.%20ICCL%2C%20being%20one%20of%20the%20associates%20of%20The%20India%20Cements%20Limited%2C%20ED%20officials%20raised%20certain%20queries%20with%20us%20and%20we%20have%20provided%20necessary%20clarifications%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710679427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F06200018%2FScreenshot-2022-05-06-at-8.00.11-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdmk-got-at-least-rs-504-crore-from-future-gaming-group-in-electoral-bonds-ec-data-reveals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20DMK%20got%20at%20least%20Rs%20504%20crore%20from%20Future%20Gaming%20Group%2C%20India%20Cement%20Limited-owned%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20Cricket%20Limited%2C%20whose%20associate%20company%20was%20raided%20by%20ED%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20had%20donated%20Rs%205%20crores%20to%20AIDMK%20in%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdmk-got-at-least-rs-504-crore-from-future-gaming-group-in-electoral-bonds-ec-data-reveals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Czechs%20struggle%20to%20contain%20surge%20of%20whooping%20cough%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710679386000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FE8CA%2Fproduction%2F_132949595_gettyimages-1140145923.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68591537%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prague's%20elderly%20mayor%20coughs%20and%20splutters%20during%20a%20public%20meeting%20as%20authorities%20battle%20increase.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68591537%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68591537.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68591537.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Views%20on%20Political%20Funding%20Foreshadowed%20Crony%20Capitalism%20in%20New%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FModi-Adani-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20enormous%20amount%20of%20money%20was%20amassed%20from%20companies%20through%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20they%20were%20profitable%20or%20incurring%20losses%2C%20facilitated%20by%20the%20removal%20of%20the%207.5%25%20limit%20on%20the%20average%20of%20three%20years%E2%80%99%20profit%20that%20could%20be%20used%20for%20funding%20political%20parties.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20alone%20has%20accumulated%20approximately%20Rs%206%2C600%20crores%2C%20significantly%20more%20than%20what%20other%20national%20and%20regional%20parties%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20and%20other%20details%20of%20such%20funding%20was%20kept%20hidden%20from%20the%20public%20%E2%80%93%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20fundamental%20right%20to%20information%20as%20well%20as%20the%20right%20to%20make%20an%20informed%20choice%20before%20casting%20their%20votes.%20Curiously%2C%20only%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20had%20access%20to%20the%20sources%20and%20details%20regarding%20the%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20its%20landmark%20judgement%2C%20declared%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20as%20unconstitutional%20and%20held%20that%20it%20created%20conditions%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpermitting%20the%20unregulated%20influence%20of%20companies%20in%20the%20governance%20and%20political%20process%20violating%20the%20principle%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%E2%80%9D%20Such%20categorical%20indictment%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%20is%20a%20first%20of%20its%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20political%20funding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20regime%20made%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%20completely%20opaque%20by%20the%20instrumentality%20of%20law%2C%20impairing%20a%20fair%20and%20free%20election%20process.%20To%20assess%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20vitiated%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20one%20must%20place%20this%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20Congress%20getting%20funds%20from%20business%20houses%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20early%20as%201931%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20worried%20that%20political%20parties%20might%20expend%20a%20disproportionately%20high%20amount%20of%20money%20for%20what%20he%20called%20%E2%80%9Cmanaging%20elections%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20illuminating%20to%20recall%20that%20on%20September%2017%2C%201931%2C%20while%20attending%20the%20second%20round%20table%20conference%20in%20London%2C%20he%20expressed%20grave%20concern%20that%20political%20parties%20would%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20using%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20only%20on%20managing%20elections%20and%20very%20critically%20remarked%20that%20that%20a%20candidate%20spending%20Rs%2060%2C000-1%20lakh%20for%20contesting%20elections%20in%20a%20poor%20country%20like%20India%20would%20be%20nothing%20but%20atrocious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20Gandhi%20been%20alive%2C%20and%20seen%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20was%20made%20in%20to%20law%20by%20committing%20multiple%20unconstitutional%20measures%20%E2%80%93%20involving%20amendments%20to%20Companies%20Act%20of%202013%2C%20Representation%20of%20People%20Act%2C%20RBI%20Act%20and%20Income%20Tax%20Act%20%E2%80%93%20he%20would%20have%20been%20aghast%20that%20what%20he%20apprehended%20in%201931%20had%20come%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20expressing%20his%20anxieties%20about%20the%20staggering%20expenditure%20on%20elections%2C%20Gandhi%20had%20no%20hesitation%20in%20conceding%20that%20Congress%20was%20being%20funded%20by%20business%20houses.%20It%20is%20instructive%20to%20peep%20into%20his%20interview%20with%20American%20journalist%20Louis%20Fischer%2C%20who%2C%20in%201942%2C%20wanted%20a%20clarification%20from%20Gandhi%20on%20the%20accusations%20that%20Congress%20was%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20big%20business%20houses%20and%20that%20he%20himself%20was%20being%20given%20money%20by%20Bombay%E2%80%99s%20mill%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20been%20acclaimed%20for%20his%20adherence%20to%20truth%2C%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20they%20are%20true.%E2%80%9D%20He%20explained%20that%20Congress%2C%20which%20relied%20on%20contributions%20of%20four%20%3Cem%3Eannas%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20year%2C%20found%20the%20amounts%20collected%20from%20its%20member%20quite%20inadequate%20for%20implementing%20its%20manifold%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFischer%20then%20asked%20a%20very%20sensitive%20question%20to%20ascertain%20if%20the%20funds%20being%20given%20by%20business%20houses%20had%20contributed%20to%20alter%20and%20shape%20Congress%E2%80%99%20politics.%20Gandhi%20was%20frank%20enough%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20a%20silent%20debt%E2%80%9D.%20He%20then%20forcefully%20and%20unequivocally%20told%20Fischer%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20actually%2C%20we%20are%20very%20little%20influenced%20by%20the%20thinking%20of%20the%20rich.%20They%20are%20sometimes%20afraid%20of%20our%20demand%20for%20full%20independence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20statement%2C%20that%20there%20was%20no%20quid%20pro%20quo%20involved%20between%20Congress%20and%20big%20business%20houses%2C%20stands%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20massive%20alignment%20of%20Modi%20regime%20with%20companies%20funding%20BJP%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%20While%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20in%201942%20flagged%20the%20autonomy%20of%20Congress%E2%80%99%20politics%20from%20money%2C%20his%20comment%20on%20big%20businesses%20fearing%20complete%20independence%20revealed%C2%A0%20their%20connection%20and%20collusion%20with%20the%20British%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20historical%20insight%20form%20Fischer%E2%80%99s%20interview%20of%20Gandhi%20is%20very%20refreshing.%20It%20is%20remarkable%20to%20fathom%20the%20havoc%20caused%20by%20the%20unconstitutional%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%2C%20scripted%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20to%20critically%20evaluate%20crony%20capitalism%20sustained%20in%20a%20calculated%20manner%20as%20well%20as%20the%20quid%20pro%20quo%20between%20companies%20funding%20political%20parties%20and%20politics%20of%20BJP%20and%20other%20regimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K%20R%20Narayanan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710678615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FModi-Adani-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgandhis-views-on-political-funding-foreshadowed-crony-capitalism-in-new-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20early%20as%201931%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20worried%20that%20political%20parties%20might%20expend%20a%20disproportionately%20high%20amount%20of%20money%20for%20what%20he%20called%20%E2%80%9Cmanaging%20elections%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgandhis-views-on-political-funding-foreshadowed-crony-capitalism-in-new-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Received%20Rs%206%2C986%20Crore%20Through%20Poll%20Bonds%2C%20Highest%20Among%20All%20Parties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20received%20the%20maximum%20funds%20through%20these%20bonds%20at%20Rs%206%2C986.5%20crore%20since%20they%20were%20introduced%20in%202018%2C%20followed%20by%20West%20Bengal's%20ruling%20party%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(Rs%201%2C397%20crore)%2C%20Congress%20(Rs%201%2C334%20crore)%20and%20BRS%20(Rs%201%2C322%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20purchaser%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%2C%20donated%20Rs%20509%20crore%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20ruling%20party%20DMK%20through%20the%20now%20scrapped%20payment%20mode%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20data%20showed%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdisha's%20ruling%20party%20BJD%20was%20the%20fourth%20largest%20recipient%20at%20Rs%20944.5%20crore%20followed%20by%20DMK%20at%20Rs%20656.5%20crore%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20ruling%20party%20YSR%20Congress%20redeemed%20bonds%20worth%20nea