ersity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ahmedabad%20Police%20Commissioner%20G.S.%20Malik%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Finternational-students-assaulted-for-offering-namaz-at-gujarat-university-hostel%2Farticle67960622.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Block%20A%2C%20around%2075%20foreign%20students%2C%20who%20live%20there%2C%20were%20offering%20prayers%20at%20their%20hostel%20yesterday%20around%2010.30%20p.m.%20Some%2020-25%20people%20entered%20the%20hostel%20premises%20and%20objected%20to%20the%20international%20students%20offering%20namaz%20there%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20do%20so%20in%20a%20mosque.%20They%20argued%20over%20the%20issue%2C%20assaulted%20them%20and%20hurled%20stones.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalik%20said%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20under%20control%20now%2C%20and%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20against%2020-25%20people%20and%20they%20will%20be%20arrested%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Fintl-muslim-students-of-gujarat-university-attacked-by-hindutva-mob-over-namaz-several-hurt%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20violence%20was%20created%20by%20a%20group%20yelling%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20slogans.%20%E2%80%9CVideos%20showing%20vandalism%20and%20stone%20pelting%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20clips%20also%20showed%20damaged%20bikes%2C%20broken%20laptops%20and%20ravaged%20rooms.%20In%20some%20of%20the%20visuals%2C%20people%20are%20seen%20throwing%20stones%20at%20the%20hostel%20and%20hurling%20abuses%20at%20the%20overseas%20students.%20In%20the%20visuals%2C%20the%20international%20students%20are%20heard%20saying%20that%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cscared%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20is%20unacceptable%E2%80%9D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20portal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20there%20is%20no%20mosque%20on%20campus%2C%20t