idth%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22one%20green%20clad%20man%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d0b0ed35cc0019e4a18b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20other%20celebrators.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lived%20in%20New%20York%20City%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20but%20I%20grew%20up%20on%20Long%20Island%2C%20and%20I%20happened%20to%20be%20visiting%20my%20family%20on%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20dragged%20my%20mom%20and%20younger%20brother%20with%20me%2C%20and%20we%20headed%20to%20the%20Long%20Island%20Rail%20Road%20to%20catch%20a%20train%20to%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20all%20ready%20for%20the%20train%20to%20be%20packed%20full%20of%20revelers%2C%20but%20it%20was%20actually%20almost%20empty.%20There%20were%20just%20two%20green-clad%20people%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20we%20arrived%20at%20Grand%20Central%20Terminal%2C%20I%20began%20spotting%20more%20people%20who%20were%20festively%20dressed%2C%20including%20some%20holding%20beers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22drinking%20beers%20at%20grand%20central%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d0eaed35cc0019e4a19f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrinking%20beers%20at%20Grand%20Central.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%2C%20I%20saw%20more%20people%20dressed%20in%20green%2C%20including%20more%20than%20a%20few%20people%20with%20beers%20and%20other%20drinks.%20One%20group%20of%20guys%20had%20a%20case%20of%20Miller%20all%20ready%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20station%20was%20also%20lit%20up%20in%20green%20for%20the%20day.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22grand%20central%20lit%20up%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d14aed35cc0019e4a1d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrand%20Central%20was%20festively%20decorated.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20(relatively)%20new%20LIRR%20terminal%20at%20Grand%20Central%2C%20known%20as%20Grand%20Central%20Madison.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flirr-grand-central-train-11-billion-nyc-abundance-agenda-infrastructure-2023-2%5C%22%3Ecost%20the%20city%20%2411.1%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20construct.%20It%20opened%20in%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20once%20I%20hit%20the%202023%20parade%20route%2C%20things%20started%20to%20go%20downhill.%20I%20started%20from%20the%20end%20of%20the%20parade%20route%20at%20Fifth%20Avenue%20and%2078th%20Street%2C%20and%20it%20was%20already%20crowded.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22crowds%20by%20me%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d17bed35cc0019e4a1ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20crowds%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20parade.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2C%20our%20side%20of%20the%20street%20was.%20The%20other%20side%2C%20the%20park%20side%2C%20could%20be%20a%20little%20deserted%20at%20times%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20easy%20way%20to%20get%20across%20as%20far%20as%20I%20could%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20parade%20goes%20up%20Fifth%20Avenue%20from%2044th%20Street%20to%2079th%20Street.%20Since%20I%20live%20on%20the%20Upper%20East%20Side%2C%20I%20figured%20we'd%20start%20by%20my%20apartment%20and%20work%20our%20way%20down.%20I'm%20unsure%20if%20that%20was%20the%20best%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20the%20end%20of%20the%20parade%20route%20was%20significantly%20less%20crowded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20I%20walked%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20noticing%20all%20the%20road%20closures%20and%20no%20parking%20signs.%20It%20must%20be%20a%20nightmare%20to%20live%20by%20the%20parade%20route.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22no%20parking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d1ade4a9f30018a6bd35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENo%20parking.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nycstpatricksparade.org%2Ffaq-frequently-asked-questions%2F%5C%22%3Eover%20two%20dozen%20road%20closures%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20the%20parade%20route%2C%20which%20can%20make%20getting%20around%20in%20the%20city%20a%20total%20nightmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20I%20enjoyed%20watching%20the%20pipe-and-drum%20bands%2C%20sometimes%20the%20bagpipes%20would%20start%20playing%20after%20they'd%20already%20passed%20by.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22good%20spot%20for%20seflies%20though%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d1e0e4a9f30018a6bd54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20was%20a%20good%20spot%20for%20selfies%2C%20though.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20missed%20a%20few%20bands%20just%20because%20of%20where%20we%20were%20standing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20partially%20our%20fault%20since%20we%20picked%20the%20spot%2C%20but%20at%20least%20three%20bands%20silently%20walked%20by%20us%20only%20to%20start%20playing%20a%20block%20or%20two%20up.%20It%20was%20annoying%2C%20so%20we%20kept%20moving%20to%20try%20and%20time%20our%20stops%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20waiting%20around%20and%20staring%20at%20the%20empty%20street.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20empty%20streets%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d60be4a9f30018a6beae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20empty%20streets.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20college%20in%20New%20Orleans%2C%20so%20I've%20attended%20dozens%20of%20Mardi%20Gras%20parades%20in%20my%20time.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20there%20would%20%3Cem%3Enever%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ebe%20this%20amount%20of%20blank%20space%20during%20one%20of%20those%20parades%20between%20the%20floats%2C%20dancers%2C%20and%20marching%20bands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20this%20parade%20doesn't%20have%20floats%20and%20is%20instead%20more%20of%20a%20celebration%20of%20the%20Irish-American%20community%2C%20I%20found%20there%20was%20quite%20a%20lot%20of%20downtime%20between%20bands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20we%20continued%20downtown%2C%20I%20thought%20some%20of%20the%20groups%20of%20people%20marching%20in%20the%20parade%20looked%20like%20crowds%20who%20just%20happened%20to%20get%20on%20the%20route.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22aimless%20people%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d638ed35cc0019e4a341%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarchers.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20and%20I%20were%20perplexed%20by%20some%20of%20the%20groups%20who%20were%20marching%20in%20the%20parade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Police%20Department%20and%20New%20York%20City%20Fire%20Department%20were%20all%20dressed%20in%20their%20best%3B%20the%20marching%20bands%20and%20dancers%20wore%20eye-catching%20costumes%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20organizations%20had%20matching%20sashes%20or%20hats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20every%20so%20often%2C%20a%20group%20would%20come%20along%20looking%20like%20they'd%20snuck%20their%20way%20onto%20the%20parade%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20had%20to%20dodge%20tourists%2C%20souvenir%20sellers%2C%20and%20college%20students%20drinking%20BORGs.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22souvenir%20sellers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d664ed35cc0019e4a35a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20souvenir%20seller.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBORGs%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-borgs-black-out-rage-gallon-tiktok-college-alcohol-poisoning-2023-3%5C%22%3Ethe%20latest%20drink%20craze%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%3A%20The%20name%20stands%20for%20%26quot%3Bblackout%20rage%20gallon%2C%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20as%20Business%20Insider%20reported%2C%20they%20caused%20trouble%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversity-massachusetts-borg-drinking-trend-tiktok-viral-video-parties-ambulances-2023-3%5C%22%3Ecollege%20campuses%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20journey%2C%20I%20walked%20past%20a%20group%20of%20three%20girls%20each%20holding%20giant%20water%20jugs%20that%20were%20filled%20with%20an%20unidentifiable%20green%20liquid.%20They'd%20written%20%26quot%3BBORG%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20dodging%20tourists%2C%20people%20trying%20to%20sell%20items%20to%20those%20tourists%2C%20and%20some%20people%20who%20seemed%20drunk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20didn't%20expect%20it%20to%20get%20political%2C%20but%20between%20a%20group%20at%20Trump%20Tower%2C%20multiple%20signs%20calling%20for%20England%20to%20get%20out%20of%20Ireland%2C%20and%20a%20few%20fliers%20criticizing%20the%20police%20union%20president%2C%20it%20could%20get%20a%20little%20tense.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22trump%20tower%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d6b7ed35cc0019e4a36c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20scene%20outside%20Trump%20Tower.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20visit%20to%20last%20year's%20parade%2C%20there%20was%20a%20crowd%20of%20supporters%20waving%20flags%20and%20banners%20with%20%26quot%3BTrump%202024%26quot%3B%20on%20them%20outside%20Trump%20Tower's%20Fifth%20Avenue%20entrance.%20I%20could%20sense%20a%20bit%20of%20unease%20around%20the%20supporters%20as%20they%20were%20yelling%20loudly%20at%20both%20paradegoers%20and%20marchers%2C%20but%20nothing%20ever%20came%20of%20it%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20witnessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20multiple%20signs%20with%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3BEngland%20Get%20Out%20of%20Ireland%2C%26quot%3B%20which%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irishcentral.com%2Fopinion%2Fniallodowd%2Fengland-get-out-of-ireland-banner-nyc-patricks-day-parade%5C%22%3EIrish%20Central%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20the%20only%20political%20sign%20allowed%20in%20the%20parade%20proper.%20I%20hadn't%20realized%20it's%20been%20part%20of%20the%20parade%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20posted%20throughout%20the%20parade%20were%20fliers%20criticizing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F01%2F23%2Fpolice-union-president-patrick-lynch-challenged-00079077%5C%22%3EPatrick%20Lynch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20then-police%20union%20president%20and%20an%20aide%20to%20the%20Parade%20Grand%20Marshal.%20Fliers%20said%20he%20should%20not%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20event.%20Lynch%20retired%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20(the%20Police%20Benevolent%20Association%20of%20the%20City%20of%20New%20York)%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20by%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20Neither%20did%20the%20NYC%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20Parade%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20we%20got%20closer%20to%20Midtown%2C%20where%20the%20parade%20started%2C%20it%20got%20increasingly%20crowded.%20It%20also%20got%20more%20and%20more%20inconvenient%20to%20keep%20walking%20down%20Fifth%20Avenue%20thanks%20to%20detours.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22detours%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d6eeed35cc0019e4a383%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDetours.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20keep%20walking%20halfway%20down%20the%20block%20just%20to%20cross%20the%20street%2C%20which%20got%20old%20really%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOr%20we%20had%20to%20wait%20on%20increasingly%20long%20lines.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22increasingly%20long%20line%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d72ced35cc0019e4a391%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20lines.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20one%20of%20the%20lines%20to%20cross%20the%20street%2C%20which%20became%20increasingly%20long%20as%20the%20crowd%20grew.%20It%20took%20up%20to%2010%20minutes%20just%20to%20cross.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMarch%20in%20New%20York%20City%20isn't%20the%20most%20picturesque%20time%2C%20either.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22scaffolding%20everywhere%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d7eded35cc0019e4a3b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScaffolding%20and%20bare%20trees.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20obviously%20isn't%20the%20fault%20of%20the%20parade%20or%20its%20organizers%2C%20and%20luckily%2C%20it%20was%20relatively%20warm%20out%20last%20year%2C%20and%20it%20was%20warm%20again%20during%20the%20parade%20this%20year.%20But%20March%20in%20New%20York%20City%20can%20be%20brutal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20walking%2028%20blocks%2C%20we%20made%20it%20to%20St.%20Patrick's%20Cathedral.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20people%20were%20also%20starting%20to%20get%20a%20bit%20more%20belligerent.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22me%20at%20st%20patricks%20cathedral%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d811ed35cc0019e4a3bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESt.%20Patrick's%20Cathedral.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsaintpatrickscathedral.org%2Fhistory-heritage%5C%22%3ESt.%20Patrick's%20Cathedral%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20New%20York%20City's%20most%20famous%20landmarks.%20It%20opened%20its%20doors%20in%201879%20and%20has%20been%20open%20for%20anyone%20to%20visit%20since%20then.%20I%20couldn't%20get%20close%20to%20it%20because%20of%20where%20I%20was%20on%20the%20parade%20route%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20powerful%20to%20be%20close%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20some%20of%20the%20parade%20attendees%20were%20getting%20into%20the%20spirit%20a%20little%20too%20much.%20I%20saw%20people%20drinking%2C%20yelling%2C%20and%20swaying%20at%20this%20point%20in%20the%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20I%20was%20entertained%20by%20the%20day%20out%2C%20I%20did%20find%20the%20parade%20underwhelming%20%E2%80%94%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20compares%20to%20Chicago's%20green%20river%20or%20the%20raucous%20celebrations%20in%20Boston.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22doing%20the%20parade%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d8aaed35cc0019e4a3d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20parade.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E