icking%20and%20shoving%20people%20praying%20on%20the%20road%2C%20and%20even%20shouting%20and%20stepping%20on%20the%20prayer%20mats%20used%20by%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20parallel%20misinformation%20online%2C%20that%20a%20mob%20in%20the%20area%20had%20attacked%20the%20policeman.%20The%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDcpNorthDelhi%2Fstatus%2F1766861664933048814%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Edebunked%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tomar%20now%20faces%20disciplinary%20action.%20%E2%80%9CA%20departmental%20inquiry%20has%20been%20initiated%20against%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20NDTV%20reported%20citing%20police%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalist%20and%20Magsaysay%20award%20winner%20Ravish%20Kumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdont-hide-your-communal-prejudice-under-the-cloak-of-protecting-our-roads%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20not%20about%20not%20causing%20traffic%20jams.%20%E2%80%9CCan%20a%20blanket%20ban%20be%20imposed%20on%20all%20types%20of%20religious%20events%20on%20roads%3F%20That%20will%20more%20adversely%20affect%20hundreds%20of%20religious%20processions%20and%20events%20of%20Hindus%20which%20go%20on%20for%20several%20days.%20The%20desire%20to%20impose%20a%20ban%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20the%20demand%20for%20improved%20management%20of%20roads.%20But%20it%20only%20reflects%20the%20frustration%20towards%20a%20community%20and%20an%20insistence%20on%20spewing%20poison.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20not%20with%20namaz%20being%20offered%20on%20the%20road.%20How%20does%20it%20affect%20someone%20if%20a%20person%20offers%20namaz%20on%20a%20moving%20train%3F%20People%20have%20been%20doing%20so%20for%20ages%20and%20no%20one%20cared.%20But%20now%20a%20video%20is%20recorded%20which%20becomes%20the%20subject%20of%20debate%20on%20TV%20and%20the%C2%A0namazi%C2%A0is%20arrested.%20If%20someone%20offers%20it%20in%20the%20mall%2C%20a%20video%20is%20shot%2C%20hatred%20is%20spread%20over%20it%20and%20an%20uproar%20is%20created.%20Does%20offering%20namaz%20at%20a%20corner%20inside%20a%20mall%20or%20a%20coaching%20centre%20also%20lead%20to%20traffic%20jam%3F%20Recently%2C%20we%20saw%20passengers%20singing%20bhajans%20and%20raising%20slogans%20of%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20in%20planes%20carrying%20visitors%20to%20Ram%20temple.%20Was%20there%20uproar%20then%3F%20People%20have%20been%20doing%20bhajan-kirtan%20on%20trains%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20This%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20our%20train%20journeys.%20To%20ask%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20it%20sounds%20strange.%20Then%20people%20should%20not%20even%20play%C2%A0antakshari%C2%A0on%20the%20train.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710670252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F09110035%2F108329889.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcourt-orders-delhi-police-to-file-report-on-policeman-who-kicked-muslims-at-prayer%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20a%20sub-inspector%20was%20seen%20kicking%20muslims%20offering%20Friday%20prayers%20on%20a%20road%20in%20Inderlok%20area.%20The%2034%20second%20video%20that%20later%20went%20viral%20and%20led%20to%20the%20policeman%E2%80%99s%20suspension.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcourt-orders-delhi-police-to-file-report-on-policeman-who-kicked-muslims-at-prayer%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Moments%20after%20volcano's%20mushroom%20cloud%20filled%20the%20sky%20a%20text%20read%3A%20'Evacuate.%20Leave%20the%20area%20immediately'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710669780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F70x70%2Fskynews-iceland-volcano_6492967.jpg%3F20240317074447%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fst