n%20sold%20in%20this%20period%20and%20people%20deserved%20to%20know%20who%20had%20bought%20them%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fdirect-sbi-eci-to-disclose-details-of-electoral-bonds-worth-rs-4k-crores-sold-before-april-2019-plea-in-supreme-court-252575%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20Sunday%20(March%2017)%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Feci-backend%2Fpublic%2Fapi%2Fdownload%3Furl%3DLMAhAK6sOPBp%252FNFF0iRfXbEB1EVSLT41NNLRjYNJJP1KivrUxbfqkDatmHy12e%252FzBiU51zPFZI5qMtjV1qgjFsK5bO1Fe8raUy8r%252B3VvV91oL95to3QGFo6faxSWGKO7CSv%252B1yJkuMeCkTzY9fhBvw%253D%253D%5C%22%3Ereleased%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20which%20parties%20redeemed%20bonds%20in%20this%20time.%20However%2C%20data%20on%20the%20purchasers%20of%20these%20bonds%20is%20still%20missing%20from%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20applicant%20sought%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20share%20the%20details%20of%20bonds%20sold%20and%20redeemed%20from%20March%201%2C%202018%2C%20to%20April%2011%2C%202019%2C%20including%20the%20alphanumeric%20number%2C%20date%20of%20purchase%2C%20denomination%2C%20names%20of%20donors%20and%20parties%20to%20the%20ECI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20two%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20the%20DMK%20and%20AIADMK%20%E2%80%93%20have%20disclosed%20the%20donors%E2%80%99%20names%20in%20their%20submissions%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20which%20subsequently%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20in%20its%20submission%2C%20has%20said%20that%20the%20party%20%E2%80%9Chas%20not%20maintained%20particulars%E2%80%9D%20of%20who%20donated%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20it%2C%20since%20it%20was%20not%20required%20by%20the%20scheme%20to%20keep%20these%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20transparency%20rights%20activists%20Anjali%20Bhardwaj%20and%20Amrita%20Johri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fvoters-must-not-remain-in-the-dark-about-buyers-of-electoral-bonds-worth-rs-4000-crore%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEver%20since%20the%20data%20has%20been%20published%2C%20there%20has%20been%20intense%20public%20engagement%20with%20the%20names%20of%20purchasers%20of%20bonds%2C%20the%20value%20of%20bonds%20bought%20by%20them%20and%20the%20dates%20on%20which%20the%20bonds%20were%20purchased.%20The%20information%2C%20as%20expected%2C%20has%20brought%20to%20light%20potential%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangements.%20Yet%2C%20voters%20remain%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20the%20identity%20of%20purchasers%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20sold%20before%20April%2012%2C%202019.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20remedied%20despite%20the%20additional%20disclosures%20that%20the%20court%20has%20directed%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20to%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20while%20hearing%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20the%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20Justice%20Ranjan%20Gogoi%2C%20observed%20that%20the%20contentions%20made%2C%20%E2%80%9Cgive%20rise%20to%20weighty%20issues%20which%20have%20a%20tremendous%20bearing%20on%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20the%20country.%20Such%20weighty%20issues%20would%20require%20an%20in-depth%20hearing.%E2%80%9D%20In%20its%20interim%20order%20dated%20April%2012%2C%202019%2C%20although%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%2C%20the%20court%20directed%20political%20parties%20to%20submit%20information%20about%20electoral%20bonds%20received%20by%20them%20to%20the%20ECI%2C%20including%3A%20the%20details%20of%20donors%20of%20each%20bond%3B%20the%20amount%20and%20date%20of%20each%20bond%3B%20and%20details%20of%20the%20bank%20in%20which%20the%20bonds%20were%20credited.%20All%20of%20this%20was%20required%20to%20be%20submitted%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20by%20political%20parties%20to%20the%20ECI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A6Once%20the%20629%20sealed%20envelopes%20are%20opened%20and%20their%20contents%20disclosed%2C%20we%20will%20get%20access%20to%20information%20submitted%20by%20political%20parties%20for%20all%20bonds%20redeemed%20by%20them%2C%20including%20those%20redeemed%20before%20April%2012%2C%202019.%20While%20this%20data%20is%20significant%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20contain%20the%20names%20of%20purchasers%20%E2%80%93%20the%20holy%20grail%20of%20disclosures%2C%20which%20enable%20public%20scrutiny%20and%20tracking%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3Equid%20pro%20quo%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710669266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fec-releases-data-on-parties-redeeming-ebs-in-first-year-plea-in-sc-says-release-buyers-names-too%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20in%20its%20submission%2C%20has%20said%20that%20the%20party%20%26quot%3Bhas%20not%20maintained%20particulars%26quot%3B%20of%20who%20donated%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20it%20in%20this%20period%2C%20since%20it%20was%20not%20required%20by%20the%20scheme%20to%20keep%20these%20records.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fec-releases-data-on-parties-redeeming-ebs-in-first-year-plea-in-sc-says-release-buyers-names-too%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98You%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Manufacture%20Authenticity%E2%80%99%3A%20the%20Makers%20of%20Australian%20Series%20%E2%80%98House%20of%20Gods%E2%80%99%20Talk%20Challenging%20Stereotypes%2C%20Religion%20and%20Community%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A171066