five%20guarantees%2C%20each%20for%20%3Cem%3Eshramik%20nyay%3C%2Fem%3E%20(labour%20justice)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1768921415711879509%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Ehissedari%20nyay%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(participatory%20justice)%20on%20Saturday%20(March%2016).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20Party%20guarantees%20a%20comprehensive%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20caste%20census.%20Through%20this%2C%20the%20population%2C%20socio-economic%20condition%20of%20all%20castes%20and%20communities%2C%20their%20share%20in%20national%20wealth%20and%20their%20representation%20in%20institutions%20related%20to%20governance%20will%20be%20surveyed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said%2C%20listing%20out%20guarantees%20under%20hissedari%20nyay.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20umberella%20of%20shramik%20nyay%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1768909379800101038%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3Elisted%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1768906435981639900%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efive%20ways%20of%20doing%20this%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3Eswasthya%20adhikar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(right%20to%20health)%2C%3Cem%3E%20shram%20ka%20samman%20%3C%2Fem%3E(dignity%20of%20labour)%2C%3Cem%3E%20shahari%20rozgar%20guarantee%20%3C%2Fem%3E(urban%20employment%20guarantee)%3Cem%3E%2C%20samajik%20suraksha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(social%20security)%20and%3Cem%3E%20surakshit%20rozgar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(guaranteed%20secure%20employment).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20surakshit%20rozgar%2C%20it%20is%20targeting%20the%20contractual%20jobs%20in%20the%20public%20sector%20which%20have%20brought%20public%20government%20jobs%20to%20a%20low%20in%20the%20past%20ten%20years%2C%20with%20record%2C%20unfilled%20vacancies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20bold%20move%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20will%20stop%20contractualisation%20of%20employment%20in%20core%20government%20functions.%20Contract%20labour%20will%20be%20the%20employment%20of%20last%20resort%20only%2C%20requiring%20clear%20justification%20and%20protection%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20workers.%20Contract%20employment%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20will%20be%20required%20to%20meet%20minimum%20standards%20of%20social%20security.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20said%20it%20%E2%80%9Cguarantees%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20the%20anti-worker%20labour%20codes%20passed%20by%20the%20Modi%20Government%2C%20and%20to%20make%20suitable%20amendments%20to%20strengthen%20the%20rights%20of%20labour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fcongress-vows-right-to-health-law-for-workers-as-part-of-five-point-mazdoor-nyay-scheme%2Fcid%2F2007403%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20five-point%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20shramik%20nyay%20announcement%20completes%20the%2025-point%20guarantees%20Congress%20had%20promised.%20The%20party%20has%20already%20announced%20five%20guarantees%20each%20for%20youth%2C%20women%2C%20farmers%20and%20social%20justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.daijiworld.com%2Fnews%2FnewsDisplay%3FnewsID%3D1176252%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIANS%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Congress%20has%20said%20that%20it%20will%20also%20get%20back%20the%20Special%20Component%20Plan%20for%20SCs%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Tribal%20Sub-plan%2C%20and%20make%20it%20enforceable%20by%20law%2C%20as%20done%20by%20some%20Congress%20governments%20in%20states.%20These%20sub-plan%20ensures%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20annual%20budgetary%20allocation%20to%20be%20dedicated%20to%20SC%20and%20ST%20communities%20in%20accordance%20with%20their%20share%20in%20the%20population.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20introduced%20by%20late%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%20the%201970s%20but%20abolished%20in%202014%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20Kharge%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20will%20also%20guarantee%20protection%20for%20Adivasi%20forest%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20guarantees%20to%20resolve%20all%20pending%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20claims%20within%201%20year%20and%20establish%20a%20transparent%20process%20to%20review%20rejected%20claims%20in%206%20months.%20The%20Congress%20will%20also%20extend%20MSP%20guarantee%20to%20Minor%20Forest%20Produce%20and%20withdraw%20all%20anti-tribal%20amendments%20to%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Amendment%20Act%20and%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20is%20reported%20as%20having%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1768910150444720310%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esamajik%20suraksha%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20party%20has%20offered%20a%20guarantee%20for%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehensive%20social%20security%20for%20all%20unorganised%20workers%2C%20including%20life%20insurance%20and%20acc%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eident%20insurance.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20shahari%20rozgar%20guarantee%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20bring%20an%20employment%20guarantee%20act%20for%20urban%20areas%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20building%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20making%20cities%20resilient%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20and%20bridging%20gaps%20in%20social%20services.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20effectively%20a%20promise%20to%20extend%20the%20MNREGA%20to%20urban%20areas%2C%20a%20longstanding%20demand%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20country%20registering%20high%20levels%20of%20urban%20unemployment%20of%20late.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20has%20promised%20shram%20ka%20samman%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Ca%20national%20minimum%20wage%20of%20Rs%20400%20per%20day%2C%20which%20will%20also%20be%20the%20minimum%20for%20all%20MGNREGA%20workers%20nationally.%E2%80%9D%20The%20guarantee%20of%20swasthya%20adhikar%20will%20probably%20see%20implementation%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20law%2C%20modelled%20on%20the%20Rajasthan%20law%20enacted%20by%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20in%20the%20state%20last%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20will%20%E2%80%9Cprovide%20universal%20healthcare%2C%20including%20free%20medicines%2C%20treatment%2C%20essential%20diagnostics%2C%20rehabilitative%20and%20palliative%20care%2C%20and%20surgery.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710667804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02103657%2FF3uRFgvW8AAhDHt.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-announces-guarantees-for-workers-social-security-urban-employment-permanent-govt-jobs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%E2%80%98Shramik%20Nyay%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Hissedaari%E2%80%99%20or%20fair%20share%20completes%20the%2025%20guarantees%20that%20Congress%20has%20listed%2C%20for%20youth%2C%20women%2C%20farmers%2C%20social%20justice%20and%20now%20workers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-announces-guarantees-for-workers-social-security-urban-employment-permanent-govt-jobs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Flipkart%20valuation%20declines%20by%20over%20Rs%2041%2C000%20cr%20in%20two%20years%2C%20says%20Walmart%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710667470000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F17%2Ffull%2F1710667376-5131.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fflipkart-valuation-declines-by