F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17130717%2FGHpnMcXWsAA63hy.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20taxonomy%20of%20traditional%20Indian%20families%2C%20my%20maternal%20grandmother%20Ama%2C%20was%20an%20accidental%20matriarch.%20Ironically%2C%20this%20mother%20of%20nine%20was%20pushed%20into%20that%20unenviable%20position%20by%20her%20own%20patriarchal%20Kumaoni%20Brahmin%20community%20after%20the%20sudden%20and%20untimely%20death%20of%20her%20husband.%20She%20had%20had%20little%20formal%20education%20and%20her%20command%20over%20English%20was%20also%20somewhat%20shaky.%20But%20when%20Ama%20spoke%20about%20tradition%2C%20she%20usually%20had%20solid%20facts%20and%20wisdom%20on%20her%20side.%20Marriages%2C%20one%20of%20her%20famous%20quips%20was%2C%20may%20have%20been%20conceived%20in%20heaven%20but%20since%20they%20have%20to%20be%20solemnised%20here%20on%20earth%2C%20it%20is%20pointless%20to%20expect%20divine%20help%20in%20finding%20a%20perfect%20match%20for%20one%E2%80%99s%20child.%20Look%20at%20King%20Janaka%20of%20Mithila%2C%20the%20most%20learned%20astrologer%20and%20a%20scholar%20of%20his%20time.%20And%20did%20he%20foresee%20when%20he%20married%20his%20daughter%20Sita%20to%20a%20crown%20prince%2C%20she%20would%20be%20exiled%20to%20a%20forest%20not%20once%20but%20twice%20by%20the%20Ayodhyawallahs%3F%20And%20Ram%2C%20her%20husband%2C%20universally%20acknowledged%20as%20the%20divine%20incarnation%20of%20Lord%20Vishnu%2C%20would%20just%20look%20on%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20368px)%2085vw%2C%20368px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22368%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22449%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20Ama%20said%2C%20we%20mortals%20must%20fall%20on%20our%20own%20resources%20and%20an%20occasional%20use%20of%20guile%20and%20subterfuge%20to%20check%20in%20on%20the%20candidates%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20family%20money%20%E2%80%93%20that%20alone%20would%20keep%20their%20girl%20safe%20should%20there%20be%2C%20god%20forbid%2C%20some%20unforeseen%20development%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAma%20did%20not%20know%20Marilyn%20Monroe%20but%20she%E2%80%99d%20have%20concurred%20with%20her%20celebrated%20song%20about%20diamonds%20being%20a%20girl%E2%80%99s%20best%20friend!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20mind%20boggling%20display%20of%20affluence%20and%20socio-political%20clout%20at%20the%20recent%20pre-wedding%20ceremonials%20of%20the%20scion%20of%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20richest%20and%20his%20young%20bride-to-be%2C%20Ama%E2%80%99s%20quips%20came%20to%20mind.%20Their%20ancestral%20town%20is%20not%20the%20first%20small%20town%20to%20have%20a%20spectacular%20wedding.%20There%20have%20been%20similar%20glittering%20(though%20less%20expensive)%20weddings%20organised%20by%20various%20cash-rich%20oligarchs%2C%20Bollywood%20mega%20stars%2C%20Indian%20cricketers%20and%20politicians.%20Usually%20celebrated%20in%20exotic%20locales%20and%20Indian%20resorts%20and%2For%20abroad.%20For%20one%20particular%20wedding%2C%20a%20historic%20palace%20in%20France%20was%20booked%20and%20chefs%20and%20guests%20ferried%20in%20private%20jets%20from%20India%20and%20other%20countries.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20all%20magnified%20the%20myth%20of%20India%20having%20come%20up%20in%20the%20world%20as%20a%20rich%2C%20exotic%20and%20happening%20place%20for%20its%20moneyed%20and%20powerful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20phobias%2C%20the%20neurotic%20timidities%20and%20aggression%20that%20guide%20finding%20a%20good%20match%20from%20Ama%E2%80%99s%20era%20till%20now%2C%20remain%20intact.%20Indians%20of%20all%20classes%20are%20by%20and%20large%20still%20wary%2C%20if%20not%20totally%20outraged%2C%20by%20the%20thought%20of%20their%20young%20choosing%20their%20own%20partners%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20something%20as%20tawdry%20as%20love.%20There%20are%20apocryphal%20reports%20about%20%E2%80%98honour%E2%80%99%20killings%2C%20rise%20in%20domestic%20abuse%20and%20divorces%2C%20but%20weddings%20are%20ironically%20getting%20fatter%20and%20celebrations%20more%20and%20more%20elaborate.%20Come%20wedding%20season%20and%20among%20the%20middle%20classes%20glittering%20wedding%20invites%20pile%20up.%20No%20more%20a%20simple%20handwritten%20invite%20with%20customary%20kumkum%2C%20turmeric%20marks%20and%20rice%20inside%20the%20envelope.%20Cards%20are%20now%20a%20collectors%E2%80%99%20item%2C%20swathed%20in%20expensive%20silk%2C%20studded%20with%20crystals%20and%20inlaid%20with%20threads%20of%20gold%20and%20silver.%20The%20kangaroo-like%20pouches%20within%20the%20tea-tray%20sized%20cards%20carry%20at%20least%20half-a-dozen%20sub-invites%20that%20list%20these%20fringe%20functions%3A%20ring%20ceremony%2C%20cocktails%2C%20%3Cem%3Emehendi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Esangeet%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20god%20knows%20what%20else%20besides.%20If%20you%20look%20hard%2C%20you%20may%20spot%20the%20name%20of%20the%20couple%2C%20and%20move%20on%20to%20the%20list%20of%20parents%2C%20grandparents%2C%20great-grandparents%2C%20cousins%2C%20uncles%20and%20aunts%2C%20siblings%20(married%20or%20otherwise)%20and%20around%20a%20dozen%20nephews%20and%20nieces%20as%20folks%20that%20await%20your%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3Edarshanabhilashi%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20merciful%20presence%20(%3Cem%3Ekripakangshi%3C%2Fem%3E)%20at%20some%20half%20a%20dozen%20festivities%20associated%20with%20the%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20just%20as%20an%20editor%20mistook%20his%20team%20for%20a%20batch%20of%20serfs%20at%20his%20(and%20rarely%2C%20her)%20beck%20and%20call%2C%20family%20elders%20too%20feel%20they%20know%20all%20about%20eminently%20marriageable%20young%20in%20their%20community.%20So%20like%20writing%20the%20daily%20editorials%20(which%20few%20read)%2C%20matchmaking%20firmly%20excluded%20the%20young%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20entirely%20by%20seniors%20with%20some%20help%20from%20a%20trusted%20family%20astrologer%20and%20the%20family%20barber%20(since%20he%20regularly%20shaved%20and%20massaged%20all%20eligible%20and%20non-eligible%20males%20in%20the%20area%20and%20was%20an%20invaluable%20repository%20of%20details%20regarding%20their%20physical%20fitness%20including%20the%20state%20of%20their%20hair%2C%20teeth%2C%20eyes%20etc).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20marriageable%20ones%20being%20spied%20upon%20by%20trusted%20family%20friends%2C%20I%20recall%20Ama%20once%20dictating%20to%20me%20one%20such%20letter%20of%20%E2%80%9Cobservations%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20non-resident%20relative%20regarding%20a%20particular%20young%20man%20from%20our%20area%20who%20had%20been%C2%A0%20recommended%20by%20someone%20as%20an%20eligible%20bachelor%20to%20the%20parents%20of%20some%20unnamed%20marriageable%20girl%20from%20our%20vast%20clan.%20After%20the%20routine%20%E2%80%9CMay%20Peace%20be%20upon%20you%2C%20worthy%20of%20all%20high%20titles%2C%20Shri%20so%20and%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ama%20came%20to%20the%20point%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20you%20had%20asked%20me%20to%20check%20on%20Shri%20So%20and%20So%E2%80%99s%20Chiranjivi%20son%2C%20I%20note%20below%20my%20findings.%20Of%20course%20the%20young%20man%20has%20an%20impeccable%20lineage%20and%20counting%20seven%20generations%20from%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20side%20and%20five%20from%20the%20mother%E2%80%99s%2C%20one%20could%20detect%20no%20blood%20relationship%2C%20so%20that%20particular%20aspect%20too%20is%20taken%20care%20of.%20The%20young%20man%20is%20said%20moreover%20to%20be%20of%20a%20most%20obedient%20son%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20and%20a%20good%20earner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPhysically%20he%20is%20somewhat%20dark%20of%20mien%20and%20according%20to%20Ramnath%20Baaji%2C%20the%20barber%2C%20has%20a%20cast%20in%20one%20eye.%20As%20I%20observed%20his%20gait%20from%20my%20house%2C%20his%20left%20leg%20seemed%20a%20bit%20shorter%20than%20his%20right.%20Upon%20enquiry%20I%20learnt%20that%20his%20mother%2C%20while%20she%20was%20expecting%20him%2C%20had%20stepped%20out%20to%20see%20an%20eclipse%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20aforementioned%20anomaly.%20However%2C%20as%20a%20groom%20he%20is%20alright%E2%80%A6Don%E2%80%99t%20just%20gape%20at%20me%2C%20write%20girl%2C%20write!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20command%20was%20barked%20out%20to%20me.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20Ama%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20remonstrated%2C%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20naming%20all%20those%20awful%20physical%20defects%2C%20how%20can%20you%20say%20he%20is%20okay%20as%20a%20groom%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShut%20up!%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ama.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20are%20we%20to%20find%20fault%20in%20another%E2%80%99s%C2%A0son%3F%20And%20in%20any%20case%2C%20if%20finally%20the%20parents%20decide%20to%20marry%20their%20girl%20to%20the%20bloke%2C%20can%20you%20imagine%20how%20foolish%20that%20can%20make%20me%20look%3F%20%3Cem%3EShaadi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20girl%2C%20is%20like%20a%20sweet%20laddoo.%20You%20eat%20it%20and%20feel%20sorry%2C%20but%20if%20you%20do%20not%20eat%20it%20you%20may%20feel%20sorrier%20still!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaakhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmrinal-pande%5C%22%3EMrinal%20Pande%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20