ess-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmarkets-to-remain-volatile-amid-us-fed-rate-decision-speculations-analysts-124031700135_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmarkets-to-remain-volatile-amid-us-fed-rate-decision-speculations-analysts-124031700135_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rukhmabai%3A%20The%20Quiet%20Making%20of%20a%20Rebel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17122913%2FRukhmabai.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpted%20with%20permission%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3ERukhmabai%3A%C2%A0The%20Life%20and%20Times%20of%20a%20Child%20Bride%20Turned%20Rebel-Doctor%3Cem%3E%20by%20Sudhir%20Chandra%2C%20published%20by%20Pan%20MacMillan%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERukhmabai%E2%80%99s%20name%20takes%20us%20reflexively%20to%20her%20epochal%20defiance.%20That%20defiance%20is%20why%20we%20remember%20her%20today.%20It%20was%20a%20defiance%20that%20caught%20everyone%20off%20guard.%20It%20had%20to%20come%20about%20for%20people%20to%20believe%20that%20it%20was%20possible.%20It%20may%20as%20well%20have%20not%20come%20about.%20For%20years%20Rukhmabai%20had%20vacillated%20between%20fear%20and%20determination%2C%20despair%20and%20hope%2C%20uncertainty%20and%20clarity.%20She%20could%20have%20chosen%20either%20way.%20A%20different%20choice%2C%20and%20the%20world%20would%20not%20have%20heard%20her%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20like%20the%20other%20girls%2C%20she%20was%20docile%20and%20diffident.%20She%20did%20dream%20of%20getting%20educated%20and%20carving%20out%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20life%3B%20so%20would%20have%20many%20other%20girls%20of%20the%20day.%20She%20differed%20in%20that%20she%20made%20her%20life%20radically%20different.%20But%20there%20was%20nothing%20pre-ordained%20about%20it.%20Till%20very%20late%20it%20seemed%20that%20she%20might%20end%20up%20like%20the%20other%20girls.%20To%20recognize%20this%20is%20not%20to%20belittle%20Rukhmabai%E2%80%99s%20resolve%20which%20was%2C%20without%20doubt%2C%20out%20of%20the%20ordinary.%20It%20is%2C%20rather%2C%20to%20avoid%20futile%20romanticizing.%20Nothing%20is%20easier%2C%20and%20more%20tempting%2C%20than%20to%20make%20Rukhmabai%20larger%20than%20the%20objective%20forces%20around%20her.%20But%20individual%20successes%20are%20never%20entirely%20independent%20of%20historical%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERukhmabai%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20world%20that%20was%20astir%20with%20new%20ideas.%20These%20new%20ideas%20were%20in%20clash%20with%20traditional%20beliefs%20and%20institutions.%20Reform%20and%20orthodoxy%20were%20locked%20in%20a%20bitter%20unending%20wrangle.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20complex%2C%20confusing%20and%20dynamic%20world.%20Orthodoxy%20and%20reform%2C%20old%20and%20new%2C%20progressive%20and%20reactionary%2C%20tradition%20and%20change%20were%2C%20of%20course%2C%20words%20employed%20to%20describe%20that%20world.%20They%20were%2C%20no%20less%2C%20also%20weapons%20that%20the%20rival%20groups%20hurled%20at%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20326px)%2085vw%2C%20326px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17122754%2F41a7RmaB-L.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22326%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17122754%2F41a7RmaB-L.jpeg%20326w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17122754%2F41a7RmaB-L-196x300.jpeg%20196w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702058%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESudhir%20Chandra%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3ERukhmabai%3A%C2%A0The%20Life%20and%20Times%20of%20a%20Child%20Bride%20Turned%20Rebel-Doctor%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EPan%20MacMillan%20India%2C%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20descriptive%20terms%2C%20they%20concealed%20as%20much%20as%20they%20revealed%20of%20that%20world.%20We%20have%20seen%20in%20the%20last%20chapter%20that%20both%20Sakharam%20and%20Ranade%20were%20proponents%20of%20reform.%20But%2C%20as%20real%20flesh-and-blood%20human%20beings%2C%20neither%20of%20them%20was%20exclusively%20new%20or%20old%2C%20reformer%20or%20reactionary.%20They%20were%20both.%20To%20further%20complicate%20things%2C%20there%20were%20varying%20ways%20in%20which%20individuals%20were%20both%20new%20and%20old%2C%20reformer%20and%20reactionary.%20Ranade%20was%20more%20new%20with%20regard%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20education%3B%20Sakharam%20was%20more%20new%20in%20supporting%20widow%20remarriage.%20We%20have%20also%20seen%20that%20Rukhmabai%20was%20impacted%20more%20by%20Sakharam%E2%80%99s%20real-life%20ambivalences%20than%20by%20his%20categorical%20progressive%20precepts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20her%20ideas%20were%20also%20shaped%20by%20what%20she%20saw%20of%20the%20emerging%20world%20of%20social%20reform.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20distant%2C%20impersonal%20world.%20She%20was%2C%20for%20better%20and%20worse%2C%20located%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20it%20and%20felt%20simultaneously%20enthused%20and%20disillusioned%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20what%20she%20studied%20at%20home%20are%20not%20known.%20We%20have%20no%20idea%20of%20the%20books%2C%20newspapers%20and%20magazines%20she%20read.%20Her%20readings%2C%20probably%2C%20were%20random%20and%20miscellaneous%2C%20not%20organized%20along%20some%20kind%20of%20a%20private%20syllabus.%20She%20used%20to%20struggle%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20books%2C%20lectures%20and%20newspaper%20writings.%20Mohini%20Varde%20quotes%20Rukhmabai%20as%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%98I%20tried%20to%20read%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20books%20and%20lecture%20notes%20but%20could%20understand%20very%20little.%E2%80%991%20This%20struggle%20was%20not%20confined%20to%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20writings.%20She%20would%20also%20go%20through%20other%20texts%20that%20were%20above%20her%20level%20of%20comprehension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20random%20readings%20apart%2C%20she%20and%20her%20half-sister%2C%20Rani%2C%20were%20often%20taken%20along%20by%20Sakharam%20to%20his%20public%20lectures.%20In%20addition%20to%20providing%20new%20information%2C%20the%20lectures%20and%20ensuing%20discussions%20would%20instil%20in%20Rukhmabai%20a%20sense%20of%20the%20culture%20and%20significance%20of%20public%20debate.%20And%2C%20of%20course%2C%20she%20had%20access%20to%20that%20unique%20source%20of%20learning%20and%20reflection%3A%20frequent%20meetings%20at%20her%20place%20of%20public%20men%2C%20writers%20and%20reformers.%20She%20would%20secretly%20imagine%20being%20like%20them%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20formal%20schooling%2C%20on%20which%20Rukhmabai%20had%20lost%20out%20and%20which%20spoon-fed%20its%20beneficiaries%2C%20her%20otherwise%20cumbersome%20selfeducation%20brought%20her%20a%20special%20advantage.%20It%20obliged%20her%20to%20sift%20and%20organize%20the%20bits%20and%20fragments%20of%20miscellaneous%20information%2C%20values%20and%20ideas%20that%20she%20tirelessly%20kept%20accumulating.%20And%20this%20exercise%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20helped%20her%20forge%20her%20own%20ways%20of%20seeing%2C%20questioning%2C%20arguing%20and%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20cheerless%20isolation%20was%20an%20endless%20internal%20polylogue%20for%20this%20inquisitive%20girl.%20She%20was%20quick%20to%20realize%20that%20the%20cheerlessness%20of%20her%20existence%20was%20socially%20ordained.%20It%20was%20the%20cheerlessness%20of%20all%20her%20Indian%20sisters.%20She%20was%20human%20enough%20to%20permit%20herself%20the%20comfort%20of%20self-pity%20and%20paranoia.%20But%20she%20never%20permitted%20herself%20the%20delusion%20that%20her%20suffering%20as%20a%20girl-woman%20was%20uniquely%20her%20own.%20Every%20time%20she%20provided%20an%20account%20of%20her%20life%2C%20she%20framed%20it%20within%20the%20larger%20context%20of%20the%20sisterhood.%20She%20saw%20in%20her%20own%20predicament%20a%20community%20of%20suffering%2C%20and%20in%20that%20suffering%20a%20larger%20cause%20and%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFar%20and%20near%2C%20all%20around%20she%20saw%20girls%20inflicted%20by%20variations%20of%20her%20own%20unwarranted%20and%20needless%20suffering.%20Living%20next%20door%20was%20her%20best%20friend%2C%20Shanta.%20Daughter%20of%20the%20eminent%20Sanskrit%20scholar%20R.%20G.%20Bhandarkar%2C%20Shanta%20was%20eleven%20when%20she%20was%20married%20to%20the%20son%20of%20another%20prominent%20public%20figure%20of%20western%20India%2C%20Dr%20Bhau%20Daji.%20Two%20years%20later%20she%20lost%20her%20husband%2C%20and%20came%20to%20live%20with%20her%20father.%20Sorrowing%20Shanta%20and%20Rukhmabai%20began%20confiding%20in%20each%20other%20their%20intimate%20thoughts%20and%20feelings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShanta%E2%80%99s%20case%20showed%20Rukhmabai%20that%20subtle%20working%20of%20orthodoxy%20which%20virtually%20neutralized%20the%20possibility%20of%20resistance%20by%20its%20victims.%20Widow%20Shanta%20was%20fortunate%20that%20she%20was%20Bhandarkar%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20and%20Bhau%20Daji%E2%80%99s%20daughter-in-law%2C%20both%20stalwart%20reformers.%20In%201869%2C%20when%20Bombay%E2%80%99s%20first%20widow%20marriage%20was%20organized%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Widow%20Remarriage%20Act%20of%201855%2C%20Bhandarkar%20was%20among%20those%20who%20defied%20organized%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%20and%20attended%20the%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhau%20Daji%20did%20something%20remarkable%20even%20earlier.%20In%201862%20a%20public%20debate%20was%20organized%20to%20resolve%20the%20question%20of%20widow%20marriage.%20Among%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20reform%20party%20in%20the%20debate%20was%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20(1832%E2%80%9371)%2C%20one%20of%20western%20India%E2%80%99s%20pioneering%20social%20reformers.%20The%20orthodox%20party%20was%20led%20by%20Brijratanji%20Maharaja%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20a%20Vaishnava%20sect.%20The%20debate%2C%20predictably%2C%20ended%20in%20a%20deadlock.%20Thereupon%2C%20writing%20in%20his%20Satya%20Prakash%2C%20Karsandas%20charged%20that%20the%20Vaishnava%20Maharajas%20had%20%E2%80%98wilfully%20altered%20to%20their%20own%20advantage%20the%20fundamental%20rules%20and%20practices%20of%20their%20religion%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98systematically%20perverted%20their%20actual%20position%20(which%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20their%20bigoted%20followers%20is%20that%20of%20deified%20humanity)%20to%20the%20most%20gross%20and%20infamous%20debauchery%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710660607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17122913%2FRukhmabai.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Frukhmabai-the-quiet-making-of-a-rebel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20years%20Rukhmabai%20had%20vacillated%20between%20fear%20and%20determination%2C%20despair%20and%20hope%2C%20uncertainty%20and%20clarity.%20She%20could%20have%20chosen%20either%20way.%20A%20different%20choice%2C%20and%20the%20world%20would%20not%20have%20heard%20her%20name.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Frukhmabai-the-quiet-making-of-a-rebel%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Panel%20of%20Five%20Scholars%20Will%20Be%20Monitoring%20India's%202024%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16163914%2F2048px-BMC_Election_2012_-_Ink_mark_after_voting_6886404209.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20Indian%20citizens%20will%20elect%20their%20political%20representatives%20for%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20upcoming%20months%2C%20five%20scholars%20based%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20have%20come%20together%20to%20form%20a%20dedicated%20panel%20to%20monitor%20the%20polls.%20The%20group%20plans%20to%20point%20out%20possible%20violations%20in%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20and%20whether%20there%20is%20an%20erosion%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20political%20parties%20and%20voters%20from%20different%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20an%20understanding%20that%20the%20use%20of%20money%2C%20muscle%20and%20institutional%20corruption%20over%20the%20years%20may%20have%20compromised%20the%20conduct%20of%20a%20totally%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20in%20India%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20democracies%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20members%20of%20the%20panel%20believe%20that%20a%20civil%20society%20initiative%20like%20theirs%20may%20raise%20concerns%20of%20the%20citizens%20more%20pertinently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20members%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CIndependent%20panel%20for%20monitoring%20Indian%20elections%20%E2%80%93%202024%E2%80%9D%20are%20Neera%20Chandhoke%20(National%20Fellow%20at%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Social%20Science%20Research%2C%20and%20retd.%20Professor%2C%20Delhi%20University%2C%20India)%2C%20Dr%20Thomas%20Daffern%20(philosopher%20and%20historian%3B%20chairman%20of%20World%20Intellectuals%20Wisdom%20Forum%3B%20Director%2C%20International%20Institute%20of%20Peace%20Studies%20and%20Global%20Philosophy%20(France%20and%20UK)%3B%20Convenor%2C%20Commonwealth%20Interfaith%20Network)%2C%20Sakhawat%20Hossain%20(former%20election%20commissioner%20of%20Bangladesh)%2C%20Dr%20Harish%20Karnick%20(former%20professor%2C%20IIT%2C%20Kanpur)%2C%20Dr%20Sebastian%20Morris%20(former%20professor%2C%20IIM%2C%20Ahmedabad)%20and%20Professor%20Rahul%20Mukherji%20(Professor%20%26amp%3B%20Chair%2C%20Modern%20Politics%20of%20South%20Asia%2C%20South%20Asia%20Institute%2C%20Heidelberg%20University%2C%20Germany).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%2C%20in%20a%20pre-election%20report%2C%20said%20that%20the%20idea%20to%20form%20a%20group%20came%20from%20concerns%20raised%20by%20civil%20society%20groups%20regarding%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccredibility%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20to%20ensure%20a%20level-playing%20field%20between%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20address%20grievances%20of%20stakeholders%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20970%20million%20Indian%20voters%20will%20cast%20their%20votes%20in%20April-May%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCitizens%20groups%20from%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20are%20voicing%20their%20worry%20that%20elections%20will%20not%20be%20free%20and%20fair%2C%20hence%20not%20genuine.%20In%20specific%20regions%2C%20there%20is%20also%20anguish%20about%20the%20likely%20denial%20of%20elections%20as%20well%20as%20of%20exclusion%20of%20vulnerable%20groups%20from%20voting%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Csecuring%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Censuring%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%E2%80%9D%20are%20two%20cornerstones%20of%20a%20representative%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20flagged%20the%20following%20concerns%20raised%20by%20the%20Indian%20media%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20%E2%80%93%2030%20million%20Muslim%20voters%2C%2040%20million%20voters%2C%20and%20a%20number%20of%20Christians%20were%20missing%20from%20the%20electoral%20rolls%20of%202019.%20The%20report%20also%20raised%20its%20protest%20against%20the%20ECI%20and%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20conduct%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20since%202018.%20It%20said%20that%20the%20ECI%20marked%20almost%20one%20lakh%20voters%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdoubtful%20voters%20or%20D-voters%E2%80%9D%2C%20most%20of%20them%20Bengali-speaking%20Muslims%2C%20risking%20their%20right%20to%20vote.%20It%20said%20that%20that%20in%20states%20in%20territories%20like%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Assam%2C%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20has%20disadvantaged%20Muslims%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20their%20proportionate%20representation%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP-led%20central%20government%20has%20systematically%20targeted%20opposition%20parties%2C%20whilst%20it%20has%20sought%20to%20strengthen%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20hold.%20Central%20investigating%20agencies%20have%20initiated%20a%20slew%20of%20criminal%20cases%20against%20opposition%20leaders.%20According%20to%20one%20report%2C%2090%25%20of%20all%20cases%20against%20political%20parties%20since%202014%2C%20by%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigations%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20have%20been%20against%20opposition%20parties%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20panel%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20now%20defunct%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20an%20opaque%20method%20of%20collecting%20donations%20by%20political%20parties%2C%20that%20has%20led%20to%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20cornering%20almost%2050%25%20of%20the%20total%20donations%20between%202017%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20evidence%20of%20arm-twisting%20too%2C%20reports%20claiming%2030%20companies%20donated%20%2440%20million%20to%20BJP%20after%20they%20faced%20criminal%20investigations%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20panel%20said%20that%20it%20was%20worried%20about%20the%20persistent%20refusal%20of%20the%20ECI%20to%20address%20possible%20flaws%20with%20the%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVM)%20and%20demands%20to%20ensure%20100%25%20Voter%20Verified%20Paper%20and%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20during%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20that%20the%20ECI%20does%20not%20%E2%80%9Cprovide%20guarantees%20against%20hacking%2C%20tampering%2C%20and%20spurious%20vote%20injections%E2%80%9D%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20system%20was%20seen%20as%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20robust%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20flagged%20its%20concerns%20about%20the%20increasing%20propensity%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmonopolise%E2%80%9D%20the%20information%20space%2C%20exclude%20opposition%20political%20parties%2C%C2%A0%20and%20control%20Indian%20media%20and%20its%20advertisement-driven%20revenue%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPro-BJP%20actors%20also%20dominate%20social%20media.%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20IT%20Cell%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20deliberately%20stoking%20communal%20hatred%20and%20spreading%20disinformation%2C%20under%20protection%20provided%20by%20its%20top%20leadership.%20BJP-led%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20have%20also%20intensified%20their%20muzzling%20of%20independent%20media%20and%20fact-checkers%2C%20including%20through%20the%20misuse%20of%20anti-terror%20and%20national%20security%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20and%20allied%20groups%20seem%20to%20have%20doubled%20down%20on%20religious%20polarisation%20for%20electoral%20gains%20%E2%80%93%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20presiding%20over%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20January%202024%2C%20and%20the%20central%20government%20announcing%20rules%20to%20the%20discriminatory%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%202019%2C%20being%20cases%20in%20point.%20Direct%20calls%20to%20violence%20against%20Muslims%20and%20other%20minorities%2C%20continue%2C%20alongside%20dehumanising%20rhetoric%2C%20by%20influential%20leaders%2C%20in%20online%20as%20well%20as%20physical%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20noted%20the%20%E2%80%9Cemerging%20threats%20posed%20by%20AI-%20powered%20deepfake%20and%20other%20technology%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20ECI%20to%20strictly%20enforce%20%E2%80%9Cexisting%20laws%2C%20rules%20and%20model%20code%20for%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20ECI%20appears%20to%20have%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpro-government%20bias%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20way%20it%20decided%20the%20elections%20dates.%20The%20panel%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20election%20commissioners%20is%20now%20being%20done%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20empowering%20itself%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvirtual%20veto%E2%80%9D%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20then%20called%20upon%20the%20ECI%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20attentive%20to%20complaints%20where%20they%20concern%20citizens%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20universal%20suffrage%2C%20and%20on%20violations%20of%20MCC%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710658466000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16163914%2F2048px-BMC_Election_2012_-_Ink_mark_after_voting_6886404209.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpanel-of-five-scholars-will-be-monitoring-indias-2024-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20group%20plans%20to%20point%20out%20possible%20violations%20in%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20and%20whether%20there%20is%20an%20erosion%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20political%20parties%20and%20voters%20from%20different%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpanel-of-five-scholars-will-be-monitoring-indias-2024-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IHCL%20to%20expand%20skilling%20centers%20by%202025%3B%20to%20impart%20training%20to%20100K%20by%202030%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710657998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F25%2Ffull%2F1682442043-3268.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fihcl-to-expand-skilling-centers-by-2025-to-impart-training-to-100k-by-2030-124031700137_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20trying%20to%20play%20its%20part%20in%20bridging%20the%20demand-supply%20gap%20of%20skilled%20workforce%20in%20the%20hospitality%20industry%2C%20which%20has%20witnessed%20robust%20growth%20in%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20after%20the%20pandemic%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fihcl-to-expand-skilling-centers-by-2025-to-impart-training-to-100k-by-2030-124031700137_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fihcl-to-expand-skilling-centers-by-2025-to-impart-training-to-100k-by-2030-124031700137_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fihcl-to-expand-skilling-centers-by-2025-to-impart-training-to-100k-by-2030-124031700137_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Political%20Funding%2C%20Arun%20Goel's%20Resignation%2C%20CEC%20Says%20'Privacy'%20Important%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16200455%2F24ffc5eb-3f57-4e78-babc-397f22336a8f.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20surprise%20resignation%20of%20former%20election%20commissioner%20Arun%20Goel%20and%20on%20the%20need%20for%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding%2C%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20on%20Saturday%20(March%2016)%20claimed%20that%20privacy%20must%20be%20respected%20in%20these%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20political%20donations%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fprivacy-plea-on-tricky-queries-chief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar-bats-for-transparency-of-political-donations%2Fcid%2F2007399%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kumar%20said%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20makes%20public%20party%20accounts%20and%20candidates%E2%80%99%20expenditure.%20However%2C%20he%20also%20stressed%20that%20the%20privacy%20of%20donors%20should%20be%20respected.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20regards%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20the%20commission%20has%20always%20been%20in%20favour%20of%20transparency%E2%80%A6.%20In%20a%20democracy%2C%20there%20is%20no%20scope%20for%20hiding%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20has%20to%20now%20also%20ask%20and%20find%20solutions%20through%20an%20institutional%20mechanism%20where%20the%20donor%E2%80%99s%20privacy%20is%20also%20considered%E2%80%A6.%20But%20the%20unaccounted%20money%20which%20is%20used%20in%20the%20elections%20%E2%80%94%20which%20we%20try%20to%20control%20during%20elections%E2%80%A6.%20How%20do%20we%20also%20control%20donations%20in%20the%20unaccounted%20form%20is%20something%20that%20the%20entire%20nation%20has%20to%20work%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20the%20donor%E2%80%99s%20privacy%20is%20also%20protected%2C%20he%20is%20not%20harassed%2C%20how%20it%20is%20channelised%2C%20how%20it%20is%20more%20and%20more%20white.%20In%20the%20digital%20age%2C%20there%20must%20be%20a%20very%2C%20very%20less%20cash%20economy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20flip-flopping%20views%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20scheme%20and%20the%20court%20case%20against%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-commission-has-no-comments-on-landmark-verdict-on-electoral-bonds-how-it-changed-its-stance%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20documented%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20Kumar%20said%20the%20matter%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CMr%20Arun%20was%20a%20very%2C%20very%20distinguished%20member%20of%20our%20team%20and%20I%20thoroughly%20enjoyed%20working%20with%20him%20all%20the%20time.%20But%20in%20every%20institution%20somebody%20will%20have%20to%20be%20given%20the%20personal%20space%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20personal%20space%20should%20not%20be%20touched%20and%20it%20is%20insensitive%20to%20ask%20personal%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20remarks%20were%20made%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20to%20announce%20dates%20for%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20where%20Kumar%20was%20alongside%20the%20two%20new%20election%20commissioners%20appointed%20last%20week%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwho-are-the-new-election-commissioner-appointees-sukhbir-singh-sandhu-and-gyanesh-kumar%5C%22%3ESukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20and%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710657478000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16200455%2F24ffc5eb-3f57-4e78-babc-397f22336a8f.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fon-political-funding-arun-goels-resignation-cec-says-privacy-important%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20remarks%20were%20made%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20to%20announce%20dates%20for%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20where%20Kumar%20was%20alongside%20the%20two%20new%20election%20commissioners%20appointed%20last%20week%20%E2%80%93%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20and%20Gyanesh%20Kumar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fon-political-funding-arun-goels-resignation-cec-says-privacy-important%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Idea%20of%20You%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Only%20Anne%20Hathaway%20Could%20Look%20This%20Confident%20Dating%20One%20of%20Her%20Daughter%E2%80%99s%20Pop%20Idols%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710657420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FThe-Idea-of-You.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235943836%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20you%E2%80%99re%2010%2C%20it%20sounds%20like%20every%20line%20your%20favorite%20boy%20band%20sings%20is%20being%20aimed%20directly%20at%20you.%20Somewhere%20along%20the%20line%2C%20the%20illusion%20shatters.%20Teenagers%20are%20smarter%20th