%20in%20markets.%20Ahead%20of%20the%202024%20halving%2C%20it's%20been%20squarely%20in%20the%20latter%20camp%2C%20up%20over%2060%25%20year-to-date.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Magadini%2C%20the%20director%20of%20derivatives%20at%20Amberdata%2C%20said%20crypto%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Breflexive%26quot%3B%20effect%20of%20pulling%20investors%20in%20from%20the%20sidelines%20as%20they%20succumb%20to%20the%20fear%20of%20missing%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHalving%20is%20likely%20not%20a%20huge%20deal%2C%20outside%20of%20this%20reflexive%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20Magadini%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BHalving%20is%20a%20very%20well-documented%20event%20and%20nothing%20of%20surprise%20has%20actually%20changed.%20We%20knew%20about%20April%202024%20halving%20over%20a%20decade%20ago.%20Typically%2C%20new%20information%20drives%20the%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20what's%20new%20this%20year%20is%20the%20wave%20of%20demand%20from%20bitcoin%20ETFs.%20Recent%20weeks%20have%20seen%20single-day%20inflows%20into%20spot%20bitcoin%20ETFs%20topping%20%241%20billion%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBitMEXResearch%2Fstatus%2F1767807895645634867%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1767807895645634867%257Ctwgr%255E265a1fa7074690cd5cda5221296f073a9b583022%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.coindesk.com%252Fmarkets%252F2024%252F03%252F13%252Fbitcoin-eyes-74k-as-btc-etfs-see-record-1b-in-net-inflows%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBitMex%3C%2Fa%3E%20data%20shows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20independent%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20halvings%20historically%20have%20been%20like%20rocket%20fuel%20for%20bitcoin.%20In%20the%2012%20months%20after%20each%20of%20the%20prior%20three%20halvings%20in%202012%2C%202016%2C%20and%202020%2C%20bitcoin's%20price%20soared%208%2C069%25%2C%20284%25%2C%20and%20559%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20dynamic%20could%20put%20us%20in%20uncharted%20territory%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaul%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20never%20had%20both%20a%20supply%20shock%20and%20a%20demand%20shock%20at%20the%20same%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMainstream%20adoption%20via%20ETFs%2C%20she%20added%2C%20opens%20the%20door%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bexplosive%20set-up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemand%20takes%20precedence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20it's%20possible%20that%20halving%20doesn't%20impact%20bitcoin's%20price%20to%20the%20same%20degree%20it%20has%20in%20the%20past.%20The%20other%20events%20took%20place%20at%20a%20time%20when%20interest%20rates%20were%20ultra-low%20and%20speculative%20bubbles%20were%20quick%20to%20inflate%20as%20investors%20chased%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20overwhelming%20demand%20for%20the%20asset%20and%20the%20new%20ETFs%20could%20end%20up%20being%20a%20more%20important%20variable%20for%20the%20price%20of%20bitcoin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin's%20supply%20is%20ultimately%20predictable%2C%20yet%20demand%20is%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20forecast.%20Samir%20Kerbage%2C%20the%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20Hashdex%2C%20doesn't%20expect%20April%20to%20bring%20a%20%26quot%3Bsell%20the%20news%26quot%3B%20event%2C%20and%20he%20said%20the%20effects%20of%20halving%20on%20prices%20will%20be%20cumulative%20rather%20than%20immediate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20believe%20that%20future%20events%20can%20be%20'priced%20in'%20with%20bitcoin%2C%20since%20the%20major%20variable%20determining%20the%20price%20of%20bitcoin%20is%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Kerbage%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20recent%20rally%20has%20been%20driven%20by%20a%20demand%20shock%20caused%20by%20the%20inception%20of%20bitcoin%20ETFs%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20is%20a%20trigger%20for%20institutions%20and%20%5Binvestment%20advisors%5D%2C%20representing%20more%20than%2080%25%20of%20the%20US%20capital%20markets%2C%20to%20start%20taking%20bitcoin%20seriously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKerbage%20forecasts%20bitcoin%20to%20climb%20into%20the%20%24200%2C00-%24300%2C000%20range%20over%20the%20next%20two%20years%20before%20correcting%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20equilibrium%20range%26quot%3B%20between%20%24100%2C000-%24150%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Rudick%2C%20senior%20strategist%20at%20GSR%2C%20said%20he%20similarly%20expects%20that%2C%20whether%20halving%20makes%20a%20near-term%20impact%20on%20price%20or%20not%2C%20bitcoin%20is%20entering%20a%20bullish%20stretch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20future%20inflows%20to%20continue%20to%20outperform%20expectations%20given%20the%20sheer%20size%20of%20the%20US%20ETF%20markets%2C%20the%20advantages%20that%20a%20spot%20ETF%20vehicle%20provides%2C%20and%20upcoming%20inflow%20catalysts%20like%20greater%20issuer%20sales%20efforts%2C%20the%20addition%20of%20spot%20products%20to%20wealth%20manager%20product%20offerings%2C%20and%20normalizing%20GBTC%20outflows%2C%26quot%3B%20Rudick%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-halving-cryptocurrency-markets-investors-etf-spot-btc-supply-demand-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710591301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f44e9e1851e792f0efff69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-halving-cryptocurrency-markets-investors-etf-spot-btc-supply-demand-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Markets%20have%20seen%20multiple%20halvings%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20the%202024%20occurrence%20is%20particularly%20momentous%20for%20bitcoin%20amid%20the%20ETF-driven%20demand%20shock.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22prosen%40insider.com%20(Phil%20Rosen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-halving-cryptocurrency-markets-investors-etf-spot-btc-supply-demand-2024-3%2