Fconsumer-rights-1710338115.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20Supriyo%20Ranjan%20Mahapatra's%20complaint%20against%20Amazon%20for%20a%20cancelled%20order%20to%20Dinesh%20Prasad%20Raturi's%20legal%20action%20against%20Bata%20India%20for%20bag%20charges%2C%20here%20are%208%20cases%20that%20highlight%20the%20importance%20of%20consumer%20rights%20and%20awareness.%20%23WorldConsumerRightsDay%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344779%2Fworld-consumers-rights-day-landmark-judgements-consumer-law-in-india-online-orders%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20Spent%2015%20Years%20to%20Save%20One%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Sustainable%20Artforms%20from%20the%20Impact%20of%20Migration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%93%20Enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2015%20November%2C%202023%2C%20Sumanti%20Devi%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20red%20and%20white%20cotton%20saree%2C%20maintained%20a%20composed%20demeanour%20despite%20her%20excitement.%20With%20a%20job%20to%20fulfil%20and%20a%20role%20to%20embody%2C%20she%20concealed%20her%20feelings%20and%20prepared%20for%20the%20upcoming%20buzz%20at%20Jamshedpur%E2%80%99s%20Gopal%20Maidan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20tenth%20year%20of%20putting%20up%20a%20stall%20at%20Samvaad%2C%20and%20yet%20the%20jitters%20are%20very%20much%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20as%20she%20neatly%20placed%20Oraon%20paintings%20in%20her%20stall.%20She%20had%20carried%20more%20than%20100%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301456%2Faipan-girl-revives-traditional-himalayan-art-minak