0by%20being%20a%20citizen%20journalist%3B%20and%20Garima%20Siddhar%20is%20a%20lawyer%20providing%20justice%20to%20tribal%20communities.%20These%20changemakers%20are%20now%20a%20part%20of%20the%20tribal%20leadership%20programme%20alumni%2C%20which%20is%20over%20400-%20members%20strong%2C%20who%20have%20stayed%20connected%20to%20share%20their%20narratives%20of%20change%20to%20inspire%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20cultural%20lens%2C%20Samvaad%20organises%20a%20grand%20inaugural%20show%20every%20year%20at%20Gopal%20Maidan.%20This%20year%2C%20251%20%3Cem%3Enagadas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edhols%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20musical%20instruments%20reverberated%20in%20homage%20to%20Birsa%20Munda.%20The%20tribals%20adorning%20bright%20yellow%20vests%20with%20white%20%3Cem%3Edhotis%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20played%20various%20goosebump-inducing%20songs%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebonga%20taal%2C%20baika%20taal%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Esantal%20taal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDancers%20and%20singers%20participated%20in%20cultural%20performances%20as%20people%20gorged%20on%20tribal%20delicacies%2C%20shopped%20for%20vibrant%20artefacts%20(handcrafted%20by%20the%20same%20artisans%20who%20are%20selling%20them)%2C%20and%20danced%20to%20the%20tribal%20beats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20tenth%20year%20and%20I%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20Samvaad%20since%20the%20beginning.%20I%20love%20the%20energy%20here.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20highlight%20is%20selling%20our%20Oraon%20paintings%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sumanti%20Devi%2C%20a%20painter%20from%20Chhattisgarh.%20%E2%80%9CVery%20few%20people%20knew%20about%20our%20paintings%20before%2C%20but%20now%20it%20is%20more%20popular.%20Initially%2C%20it%20was%20only%20handicrafts%20stalls%2C%20but%20Samvaad%20has%20grown%20so%20much%20with%20%3Cem%3EAkhara%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20fellowship%2C%20tribal%20healers%2C%20Tribal%20Leadership%20Programme%20and%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Choisa%20Hakong%20from%20the%20Chakesang%20tribe%20(Nagaland)%20was%20at%20the%20conclave%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20%E2%80%9CSamvaad%20is%20connecting%20tribals%20as%20one%20in%20spirit%20and%20culture.%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20attend%20and%20showcase%20our%20products%20made%20from%20teak%20and%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20five%20days%2C%20Pritesh%2C%20Sumanti%2C%20and%20Choisa%2C%20along%20with%20people%20from%20110%20other%20tribes%2C%20displayed%20their%20cuisine%2C%20artwork%2C%20and%20healing%20practices.%20Besides%20the%20stalls%2C%20140%20home%20chefs%20from%2037%20tribes%20offered%20home%20delivery%20via%20the%20Zomato%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20these%20artisans%20goes%20beyond%20selling%20their%20products.%20They%20also%20refine%20their%20skills%20through%20workshops%20and%20sessions%20led%20by%20handicraft%20experts%2C%20engage%20in%20healing%20practices%2C%20and%20showcase%20their%20culinary%20talents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tribal%20food%20at%20display%20in%20one%20of%20the%20stalls%20at%20Samvaad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2