crete%20on%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20the%20resort%20uses%20very%20low%20lighting%20as%20they%20have%20four%20different%20varieties%20of%20owls%20that%20stay%20on%20the%20property.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20moment%20you%20turn%20bright%20lights%20on%2C%20they%20fly%20away.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20disturb%20the%20birds%2C%20so%20we%20give%20flashlights%20to%20the%20guests%20and%20ask%20them%20to%20use%20the%20light%20only%20when%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resort%20also%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fcsr-update%2Fnestle-indias-csr-project-hilldaari-pioneering-sustainable-waste-management-in-tourist-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20place.%20%E2%80%9CKitchen%20wastewater%20flows%20through%20grease%20traps%2C%20and%20sewage%20is%20directed%20into%20septic%20tanks%20before%20being%20taken%20through%20our%20sewage%20treatment%20plant.%20Wastewater%20flows%20into%20soak%20pits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20natural%20purification%20process%20then%20takes%20over%2C%20ensuring%20the%20groundwater%20is%20not%20polluted%20and%20the%20water%20table%20is%20undisturbed.%20We%20also%20do%20not%20take%20a%20drop%20of%20water%20from%20the%20Government%20pipeline.%20We%20harvest%20rainwater%20and%20the%20location%20we%20selected%20has%20a%20natural%20spring%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fschool-18-1709819895.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22All%20the%20cottages%20and%20common%20areas%20at%20the%20resort%20are%20made%20using%20natural%20materials%20such%20as%20wood%20and%20thatch.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetter